Sample code: Quick links: Libraries BaseObject Basic elements  
 

' Make sure we don't depend on scripting engine defaults
Option Explicit
ValidationMode  = True
InteractiveMode = im_Batch

Function DescribePdCommonProgressDialog(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Progress Dialog

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Min: "               & CStr(obj.Min             ) ' Minimum
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Max: "               & CStr(obj.Max             ) ' Maximum
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & CStr(obj.Position        ) ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stepping: "          & CStr(obj.Stepping        ) ' Stepping
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Text: """            & obj.Text            & """" ' Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Text2: """           & obj.Text2           & """" ' Second Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BarColor: "          & CStr(obj.BarColor        ) ' Bar Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackColor: "         & CStr(obj.BackColor       ) ' Background Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TextFormat: """      & obj.TextFormat      & """" ' Text Format
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Animation: """       & obj.Animation       & """" ' Animation Filename
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ConfirmMessage: """  & obj.ConfirmMessage  & """" ' Cancel Confirmation Message
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PositiveConfirm: "   & CStr(obj.PositiveConfirm ) ' Positive Confirmation
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonProgressDialog = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCommonProgressStatusBar(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Progress Status Bar

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Min: "               & CStr(obj.Min             ) ' Minimum
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Max: "               & CStr(obj.Max             ) ' Maximum
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & CStr(obj.Position        ) ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stepping: "          & CStr(obj.Stepping        ) ' Stepping
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Text: """            & obj.Text            & """" ' Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Text2: """           & obj.Text2           & """" ' Second Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BarColor: "          & CStr(obj.BarColor        ) ' Bar Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackColor: "         & CStr(obj.BackColor       ) ' Background Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CanBeCanceled: "     & CStr(obj.CanBeCanceled   ) ' Can Be Cancelled
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonProgressStatusBar = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCommonApplicationModule(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Application Module

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Library: "           & CStrObj(obj.Library      ) ' Metalibrary
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModelKind: "         & CStr(obj.ModelKind    ) ' Model Kind
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IsLoaded: "          & CStr(obj.IsLoaded        ) ' Loaded
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModuleIcon: "        & obj.ModuleIcon ' Module Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ReportClientCode: """ & obj.ReportClientCode & """" ' Report Client Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "HasTargetLanguage: " & CStr(obj.HasTargetLanguage) ' Has notion of Target Language
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LanguagesCaption: """ & obj.LanguagesCaption & """" ' Target Language Caption
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LanguagesClass: "    & CStrObj(obj.LanguagesClass) ' Target Language Class
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LanguagesDirectory: """ & obj.LanguagesDirectory & """" ' Language Definitions Directory
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtensionsDirectory: """ & obj.ExtensionsDirectory & """" ' Extension Definitions Directory
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UserModelTemplatesDirectory: """ & obj.UserModelTemplatesDirectory & """" ' Model Templates Directory
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ReportTemplatesDirectory: """ & obj.ReportTemplatesDirectory & """" ' Report Templates Directory
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultLanguage: "   & CStrObj(obj.DefaultLanguage) ' Default Language Class
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultDiagram: "    & CStrObj(obj.DefaultDiagram) ' Default Diagram Class
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CanCreateNewModel: " & CStr(obj.CanCreateNewModel) ' Can Create New Model
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonApplicationModule = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCommonResourceFile(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Resource File

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Filename: """        & obj.Filename        & """" ' Filename
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AutoAttach: "        & CStr(obj.AutoAttach      ) ' Automatic Attachment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Category: """        & obj.Category        & """" ' Category
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Family: """          & obj.Family          & """" ' Family
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ID: """              & obj.ID              & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Module: "            & CStrObj(obj.Module       ) ' Module
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubFamily: """       & obj.SubFamily       & """" ' Subfamily
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ResourceKind: "      & CStr(obj.ResourceKind ) ' Target Class Kind
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ResourceClass: "     & CStrObj(obj.ResourceClass) ' Target Class
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonResourceFile = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCommonMetaModel(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Metamodel

      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then

      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Version: """         & obj.Version         & """" ' Metamodel Version

   End If

End Function 

Function DescribePdCommonMetaLibrary(obj)

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PublicName: """      & obj.PublicName      & """" ' Public Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LocalizedName: """   & obj.LocalizedName   & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaModel: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaModel    ) ' Owning Metamodel
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonMetaLibrary = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCommonMetaAttribute(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Metaattribute

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PublicName: """      & obj.PublicName      & """" ' Public Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LocalizedName: """   & obj.LocalizedName   & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MemberFlags: "       & CStr(obj.MemberFlags     ) ' Member Flags
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Readonly: "          & CStr(obj.Readonly        ) ' Read-only
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Calculated: "        & CStr(obj.Calculated      ) ' Calculated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Alias: "             & CStr(obj.Alias           ) ' Alias
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AliasBase: "         & CStrObj(obj.AliasBase    ) ' Alias Base
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MemberClass: "       & CStrObj(obj.MemberClass  ) ' Owning Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Type: "              & CStr(obj.Type            ) ' Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TypeName: """        & obj.TypeName        & """" ' Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Attribute Flags
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Default: "           & CStr(obj.Default      ) ' Default Value
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationClassKind: " & CStr(obj.DestinationClassKind) ' Target Class Kind
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "HasListOfValues: "   & CStr(obj.HasListOfValues ) ' Has List Of Values
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "HasConstantListOfValues: " & CStr(obj.HasConstantListOfValues) ' Has Constant List Of Values
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "HasOrderedListOfValues: " & CStr(obj.HasOrderedListOfValues) ' Has Sorted List Of Values
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "HasListOfObjects: "  & CStr(obj.HasListOfObjects) ' Has List Of Objects
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "HasConstantListOfObjects: " & CStr(obj.HasConstantListOfObjects) ' Has Constant List Of Objects
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ControlType: "       & CStr(obj.ControlType     ) ' Control Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ControlWindowStyles: " & CStr(obj.ControlWindowStyles) ' Control Window Style Flags
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ControlWindowStylesEx: " & CStr(obj.ControlWindowStylesEx) ' Control Window Extended Style Flags
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ControlDefaultGridSize: " & CStr(obj.ControlDefaultGridSize) ' Control Default Grid Size
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonMetaAttribute = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCommonMetaCollection(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Metacollection

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PublicName: """      & obj.PublicName      & """" ' Public Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LocalizedName: """   & obj.LocalizedName   & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MemberFlags: "       & CStr(obj.MemberFlags     ) ' Member Flags
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Readonly: "          & CStr(obj.Readonly        ) ' Read-only
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Calculated: "        & CStr(obj.Calculated      ) ' Calculated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Alias: "             & CStr(obj.Alias           ) ' Alias
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AliasBase: "         & CStrObj(obj.AliasBase    ) ' Alias Base
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MemberClass: "       & CStrObj(obj.MemberClass  ) ' Owning Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ContentClass: "      & CStrObj(obj.ContentClass ) ' Class of objects within Collection
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ContentKind: "       & CStr(obj.ContentKind  ) ' Kind of objects within Collection
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Collection Flags
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Inverse: "           & CStr(obj.Inverse         ) ' Inverse
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Composition: "       & CStr(obj.Composition     ) ' Composition
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Delete: "            & CStr(obj.Delete          ) ' Delete
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Copy: "              & CStr(obj.Copy            ) ' Copy
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Ordered: "           & CStr(obj.Ordered         ) ' Ordered
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonMetaCollection = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCommonMetaClass(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Metaclass

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PublicName: """      & obj.PublicName      & """" ' Public Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LocalizedName: """   & obj.LocalizedName   & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "QualifiedPublicName: """ & obj.QualifiedPublicName & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DeprecatedName: """  & obj.DeprecatedName  & """" ' Deprecated Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Kind: "              & CStr(obj.Kind         ) ' Kind
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Class Flags
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Abstract: "          & CStr(obj.Abstract        ) ' Abstract
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "InstancesIconPicture: " & obj.InstancesIconPicture ' Instances icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Library: "           & CStrObj(obj.Library      ) ' Owning Library
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ParentClass: "       & CStrObj(obj.ParentClass  ) ' Parent Metaclass
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonMetaClass = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCommonShortcut(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Shortcut

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "External: "          & CStr(obj.External        ) ' Is External
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TargetType: """      & obj.TargetType      & """" ' Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TargetModel: "       & CStrObj(obj.TargetModel  ) ' Target Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TargetPackage: "     & CStrObj(obj.TargetPackage) ' Target Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Status: """          & obj.Status          & """" ' Status
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TargetObject: "      & CStrObj(obj.TargetObject ) ' Target Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TargetID: """        & obj.TargetID        & """" ' Target Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TargetClassKind: "   & CStr(obj.TargetClassKind ) ' Target Object Class Kind
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TargetPackagePath: """ & obj.TargetPackagePath & """" ' Target Object Package Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TargetShortDescription: """ & obj.TargetShortDescription & """" ' Target Object Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TargetStereotype: """ & obj.TargetStereotype & """" ' Target Object Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TargetStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.TargetStereotypeObject) ' Target Object Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolDisplayed: "   & CStr(obj.SymbolDisplayed ) ' Has Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FullPath: """        & obj.FullPath        & """" ' Full path without Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortPath: """       & obj.ShortPath       & """" ' Short path without Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TargetModelDefinition: " & CStrObj(obj.TargetModelDefinition) ' Target Model Definition
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Used: "              & CStr(obj.Used            ) ' Used
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LastLoadFailed: "    & CStr(obj.LastLoadFailed  ) ' Last Load Failed
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Generated: "         & CStr(obj.Generated       ) ' Generate
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationType: "    & CStr(obj.GenerationType  ) ' Generation Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkSource: "        & CStrObj(obj.LinkSource   ) ' Source Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkDestination: "   & CStrObj(obj.LinkDestination) ' Destination Object
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonShortcut = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCommonTargetModel(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Target model reference

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TargetModelType: """ & obj.TargetModelType & """" ' Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TargetModelFileName: """ & obj.TargetModelFileName & """" ' File Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Status: """          & obj.Status          & """" ' Status
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Used: "              & CStr(obj.Used            ) ' Used
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TargetModelURL: """  & obj.TargetModelURL  & """" ' Target Model URL
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TargetModelID: """   & obj.TargetModelID   & """" ' Target Model ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TargetModelClassID: """ & obj.TargetModelClassID & """" ' Target Model CLSID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TargetModelClassKind: " & CStr(obj.TargetModelClassKind) ' Target Model Kind
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TargetModelObject: " & CStrObj(obj.TargetModelObject) ' Target Model Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LastLoadFailed: "    & CStr(obj.LastLoadFailed  ) ' Last Load Failed
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonTargetModel = Desc

End Function

Function DescribePdCommonPolygonSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Polygon

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfPoints: "      & obj.ListOfPoints.AsText     ' List Points
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CornerStyle: "       & CStr(obj.CornerStyle     ) ' Corner Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ArrowStyle: "        & CStr(obj.ArrowStyle      ) ' Arrows
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkPosition: "      & obj.LinkPosition.AsText     ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkSize: "          & obj.LinkSize.AsText         ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BrushStyle: "        & CStr(obj.BrushStyle      ) ' Brush Style

   End If

' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Arc

   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonArcSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCommonRectangleSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Rectangle

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BrushStyle: "        & CStr(obj.BrushStyle      ) ' Brush Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientFillMode: "  & CStr(obj.GradientFillMode) ' Gradient Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientEndColor: "  & CStr(obj.GradientEndColor) ' Gradient End Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PictureFillMode: "   & CStr(obj.PictureFillMode ) ' Picture Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AutoAdjustToText: "  & CStr(obj.AutoAdjustToText) ' Auto Adjust to Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ManuallyResized: "   & CStr(obj.ManuallyResized ) ' Resized
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepAspect: "        & CStr(obj.KeepAspect      ) ' Keep Aspect Ratio
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepCenter: "        & CStr(obj.KeepCenter      ) ' Keep Center
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepSize: "          & CStr(obj.KeepSize        ) ' Keep Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureType: " & CStr(obj.CustomPictureType) ' Custom Picture Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomTextMode: "    & CStr(obj.CustomTextMode  ) ' Custom Picture Text Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureID: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureID & """" ' Background Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureID: """ & obj.CustomPictureID & """" ' Custom Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureFile: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureFile & """" ' Background Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureFile: """ & obj.CustomPictureFile & """" ' Custom Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomShapeType: "   & CStr(obj.CustomShapeType ) ' Custom Shape Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Text: """            & obj.Text            & """" ' String
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TextStyle: "         & CStr(obj.TextStyle       ) ' Text Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FontColor: "         & CStr(obj.FontColor       ) ' Font Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FontName: """        & obj.FontName        & """" ' Font Name
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonRectangleSymbol = Desc

End Function

   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonRoundRectangleSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCommonEllipseSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Ellipse

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BrushStyle: "        & CStr(obj.BrushStyle      ) ' Brush Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientFillMode: "  & CStr(obj.GradientFillMode) ' Gradient Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientEndColor: "  & CStr(obj.GradientEndColor) ' Gradient End Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PictureFillMode: "   & CStr(obj.PictureFillMode ) ' Picture Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AutoAdjustToText: "  & CStr(obj.AutoAdjustToText) ' Auto Adjust to Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ManuallyResized: "   & CStr(obj.ManuallyResized ) ' Resized
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepAspect: "        & CStr(obj.KeepAspect      ) ' Keep Aspect Ratio
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepCenter: "        & CStr(obj.KeepCenter      ) ' Keep Center
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepSize: "          & CStr(obj.KeepSize        ) ' Keep Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureType: " & CStr(obj.CustomPictureType) ' Custom Picture Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomTextMode: "    & CStr(obj.CustomTextMode  ) ' Custom Picture Text Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureID: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureID & """" ' Background Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureID: """ & obj.CustomPictureID & """" ' Custom Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureFile: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureFile & """" ' Background Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureFile: """ & obj.CustomPictureFile & """" ' Custom Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomShapeType: "   & CStr(obj.CustomShapeType ) ' Custom Shape Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Text: """            & obj.Text            & """" ' String
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TextStyle: "         & CStr(obj.TextStyle       ) ' Text Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FontColor: "         & CStr(obj.FontColor       ) ' Font Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FontName: """        & obj.FontName        & """" ' Font Name
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonEllipseSymbol = Desc

End Function

Function DescribePdCommonLinkSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Link Symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfPoints: "      & obj.ListOfPoints.AsText     ' List Points

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkPosition: "      & obj.LinkPosition.AsText     ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkSize: "          & obj.LinkSize.AsText         ' Size

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationSymbol: " & CStrObj(obj.DestinationSymbol) ' Destination Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CenterTextOffset: "  & obj.CenterTextOffset.AsText ' Centered Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceTextOffset: "  & obj.SourceTextOffset.AsText ' Source Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationTextOffset: " & obj.DestinationTextOffset.AsText ' Destination Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TextStyle: "         & CStr(obj.TextStyle       ) ' Text Style

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceText: """      & obj.SourceText      & """" ' Source Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationText: """ & obj.DestinationText & """" ' Destination Text
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonLinkSymbol = Desc

End Function

   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Blob: """            & obj.Blob            & """" ' Blob
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Blob: """            & obj.Blob            & """" ' Blob
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureID: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureID & """" ' Background Picture ID
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonBitmapSymbol = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureFile: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureFile & """" ' Background Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureFile: """ & obj.CustomPictureFile & """" ' Custom Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomShapeType: "   & CStr(obj.CustomShapeType ) ' Custom Shape Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Text: """            & obj.Text            & """" ' String
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TextStyle: "         & CStr(obj.TextStyle       ) ' Text Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FontColor: "         & CStr(obj.FontColor       ) ' Font Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FontName: """        & obj.FontName        & """" ' Font Name
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonSwimlaneSubGroupSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCommonPictureFile(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Picture File

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Picture Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PictureID: """       & obj.PictureID       & """" ' Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PictureType: "       & CStr(obj.PictureType     ) ' Picture Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Path: """            & obj.Path            & """" ' Picture Path
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonPictureFile = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SpaceBetweenTextAndRightBorder: " & CStr(obj.SpaceBetweenTextAndRightBorder) ' Space Between Text and Right Border

   Else

   End If

      Desc = "<Empty!>"

         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Image: "             & CStr(obj.Image           ) ' Image
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExpandedImage: "     & CStr(obj.ExpandedImage   ) ' Expanded Image

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ItemModuleID: """    & obj.ItemModuleID    & """" ' Item Module ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Label: """           & obj.Label           & """" ' Label

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedDefaultTitle: """ & obj.ExtendedDefaultTitle & """" ' Extended Default Title
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TitlePath: """       & obj.TitlePath       & """" ' Title Extended Path
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ItemKind: "          & CStr(obj.ItemKind        ) ' Item Class Kind

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "NumberOfItems: "     & CStr(obj.NumberOfItems   ) ' Number of Items
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ItemIndex: "         & CStr(obj.ItemIndex       ) ' Item Index
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UserParameter: "     & CStr(obj.UserParameter   ) ' User Parameter
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShowTitle: "         & CStr(obj.ShowTitle       ) ' Show Title
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CollectionName: """  & obj.CollectionName  & """" ' Collection Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShowGroupInHTMLToc: " & CStr(obj.ShowGroupInHTMLToc) ' Show Item in TOC
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Text: """            & obj.Text            & """" ' Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ImplicitOrder: "     & CStr(obj.ImplicitOrder   ) ' User Order
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShowSubItemsInHTMLToc: " & CStr(obj.ShowSubItemsInHTMLToc) ' Show Contained Items in HTML TOC
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonBookTitleReportItem = Desc

End Function

   End If

Function DescribePdCommonAttributeTextReportItem(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Group Text

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ItemContainer: "     & CStr(obj.ItemContainer   ) ' Is Item Container
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AvailableLabel: """  & obj.AvailableLabel  & """" ' Label
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TemplateLabel: """   & obj.TemplateLabel   & """" ' Label
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ParentBookKind: "    & CStr(obj.ParentBookKind  ) ' Parent Book Kind
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ParentBookStereotype: """ & obj.ParentBookStereotype & """" ' Parent Book Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ContainsData: "      & CStr(obj.ContainsData    ) ' Contains Data
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayParentTitle: " & CStr(obj.DisplayParentTitle) ' 
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ItemTOCEntry: "      & CStr(obj.ItemTOCEntry    ) ' Is Item TOC Entry
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ItemInTemplate: "    & CStr(obj.ItemInTemplate  ) ' Is Item in Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ItemModified: "      & CStr(obj.ItemModified    ) ' Is Item Modified
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LanguageSection: "   & CStr(obj.LanguageSection ) ' Language Section
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Image: "             & CStr(obj.Image           ) ' Image
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExpandedImage: "     & CStr(obj.ExpandedImage   ) ' Expanded Image
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ItemRegistrationID: """ & obj.ItemRegistrationID & """" ' Item Registration ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ItemModuleID: """    & obj.ItemModuleID    & """" ' Item Module ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Label: """           & obj.Label           & """" ' Label
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayFlag: "       & CStr(obj.DisplayFlag     ) ' Display Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayTitle: """    & obj.DisplayTitle    & """" ' Title
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedDefaultTitle: """ & obj.ExtendedDefaultTitle & """" ' Extended Default Title
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TitlePath: """       & obj.TitlePath       & """" ' Title Extended Path
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ItemKind: "          & CStr(obj.ItemKind        ) ' Item Class Kind
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TitleResourceID: "   & CStr(obj.TitleResourceID ) ' Title Resource ID

      End If
   Else

   End If

   DescribePdCommonAttributeTextReportItem = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCommonReportCardCell(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Form Cell Definition

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TitlePath: """       & obj.TitlePath       & """" ' Column Title Path
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultTableCellText: """ & obj.DefaultTableCellText & """" ' Default Table Cell Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StringResourceID: "  & CStr(obj.StringResourceID) ' String Resource ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TextTableResource: """ & obj.TextTableResource & """" ' Text Table Resource

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ItemKeyword: "       & CStr(obj.ItemKeyword     ) ' Is Item Keyword
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TitleCell: "         & CStr(obj.TitleCell       ) ' Is Cell a Title
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "VerticalAlignment: " & CStr(obj.VerticalAlignment) ' Vertical Alignment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BorderType: "        & CStr(obj.BorderType      ) ' Border Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BorderWidth: "       & CStr(obj.BorderWidth     ) ' Border Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Enabled: "           & CStr(obj.Enabled         ) ' Enabled
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonReportCardCell = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height of Row
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LeftIndentation: "   & CStr(obj.LeftIndentation ) ' Left Indentation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AllowBreak: "        & CStr(obj.AllowBreak      ) ' Allow Break Row 
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Alignment: "         & CStr(obj.Alignment       ) ' Row Alignment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SpaceBetweenCells: " & CStr(obj.SpaceBetweenCells) ' Space Between Cells
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Header: "            & CStr(obj.Header          ) ' Is the Row a Header Row
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Footer: "            & CStr(obj.Footer          ) ' Is the Row a Footer Row

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Row: """             & obj.Row             & """" ' Row
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonReportCardRow = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ContainsData: "      & CStr(obj.ContainsData    ) ' Contains Data

Function DescribePdCommonListCellDefinition(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon List Cell Definition

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ItemKeyword: "       & CStr(obj.ItemKeyword     ) ' Is Item Keyword

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "VerticalAlignment: " & CStr(obj.VerticalAlignment) ' Vertical Alignment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BorderType: "        & CStr(obj.BorderType      ) ' Border Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BorderWidth: "       & CStr(obj.BorderWidth     ) ' Border Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Enabled: "           & CStr(obj.Enabled         ) ' Enabled

      End If
   Else

   End If

   Else

   End If

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator

Function DescribePdCommonTitleReportItem(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Title

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else

Function DescribePdCommonReportAvailableItemsContainer(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Available items container

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ItemContainer: "     & CStr(obj.ItemContainer   ) ' Is Item Container
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AvailableLabel: """  & obj.AvailableLabel  & """" ' Label
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TemplateLabel: """   & obj.TemplateLabel   & """" ' Label
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ParentBookKind: "    & CStr(obj.ParentBookKind  ) ' Parent Book Kind

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ItemTOCEntry: "      & CStr(obj.ItemTOCEntry    ) ' Is Item TOC Entry
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ItemInTemplate: "    & CStr(obj.ItemInTemplate  ) ' Is Item in Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ItemModified: "      & CStr(obj.ItemModified    ) ' Is Item Modified
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LanguageSection: "   & CStr(obj.LanguageSection ) ' Language Section
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Image: "             & CStr(obj.Image           ) ' Image
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExpandedImage: "     & CStr(obj.ExpandedImage   ) ' Expanded Image

   Else

   End If

End Function

      End If
   Else

   End If

   DescribePdCommonBaseReport = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModelFilePath: """   & obj.ModelFilePath   & """" ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ApplyTemplate: "     & CStr(obj.ApplyTemplate   ) ' Apply Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModelFilename: """   & obj.ModelFilename   & """" ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TargetModel: "       & CStrObj(obj.TargetModel  ) ' TargetModel
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectSelection: """ & obj.ObjectSelection & """" ' Object Selection for Section
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModelID: """         & obj.ModelID         & """" ' Model ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TemplateFileName: """ & obj.TemplateFileName & """" ' Template
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonReportSection = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCommonIntraModelReport(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Intra-Model Report

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ReportFirstPageAuthor: """ & obj.ReportFirstPageAuthor & """" ' Report First Page Author
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ReportFirstPageVersion: """ & obj.ReportFirstPageVersion & """" ' Report First Page Version
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ReportFirstPageDate: """ & obj.ReportFirstPageDate & """" ' Report First Page Date

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FirstPageDefined: "  & CStr(obj.FirstPageDefined) ' Does the Report Have a First Page

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FirstPageAuthorDefined: " & CStr(obj.FirstPageAuthorDefined) ' Does the Report Have a First Page Author
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FirstPageVersionDefined: " & CStr(obj.FirstPageVersionDefined) ' Does the Report Have a First Page Version
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FirstPageDateDefined: " & CStr(obj.FirstPageDateDefined) ' Does the Report Have a First Page Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FirstPageSummaryDefined: " & CStr(obj.FirstPageSummaryDefined) ' Does the Report Have a First Page Summary
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "HtmlTemplate: """    & obj.HtmlTemplate    & """" ' HTML Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "HtmlStylesheetFile: """ & obj.HtmlStylesheetFile & """" ' Report HTML Stylesheet File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "HtmlHeaderFile: """  & obj.HtmlHeaderFile  & """" ' Report HTML Header Frame File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "HtmlFooterFile: """  & obj.HtmlFooterFile  & """" ' Report HTML Footer Frame File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "HtmlHomePageFile: """ & obj.HtmlHomePageFile & """" ' Report HTML Home Page File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "HtmlHeaderSize: "    & CStr(obj.HtmlHeaderSize  ) ' Report HTML Header Frame Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "HtmlFooterSize: "    & CStr(obj.HtmlFooterSize  ) ' Report HTML Footer Frame Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "HtmlTOCRighttoLeft: " & CStr(obj.HtmlTOCRighttoLeft) ' HTML TOC Right to Left

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RtfUseSectionHeadFoot: " & CStr(obj.RtfUseSectionHeadFoot) ' Use Section Header and Footer

   End If

   Else

   End If
