End Function 

Function DescribePdCommonExtendedDependency(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Extended Dependency

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object2: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object2      ) ' Second Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object1: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object1      ) ' First Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkDirection: "     & CStr(obj.LinkDirection   ) ' Direction
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExternalDependenciesText: """ & obj.ExternalDependenciesText & """" ' External Dependencies Blob
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "InfluentObject: "    & CStrObj(obj.InfluentObject) ' Influent Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DependentObject: "   & CStrObj(obj.DependentObject) ' Dependent Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayedStereotype: """ & obj.DisplayedStereotype & """" ' Extended Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "InfluentObjectType: """ & obj.InfluentObjectType & """" ' Influent Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "InfluentModel: """   & obj.InfluentModel   & """" ' Influent Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "InfluentPackage: """ & obj.InfluentPackage & """" ' Influent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DependentObjectType: """ & obj.DependentObjectType & """" ' Dependent Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonExtendedDependency = Desc

End Function

Function DescribePdCommonExtendedSubObject(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Extended Sub-Object

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object

   End If

Function DescribePdCommonExtendedLink(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Extended Link

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object2: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object2      ) ' Second Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object1: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object1      ) ' First Object
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonExtendedLink = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Label: """           & obj.Label           & """" ' Label
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DataType: "          & CStr(obj.DataType        ) ' Data Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Value: """           & obj.Value           & """" ' Value
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Template: "          & CStr(obj.Template        ) ' Template

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Complete: "          & CStr(obj.Complete        ) ' Complete

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ComputedAccessType: """ & obj.ComputedAccessType & """" ' Computed Access Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationStereotype: """ & obj.DestinationStereotype & """" ' Target Stereotype

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SetMethodScript: """ & obj.SetMethodScript & """" ' Set Method Script

   Else

   End If

Function DescribePdCommonExtendedCollectionTargetItem(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Extended Collection

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Type: "              & CStr(obj.Type            ) ' Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ItemPath: """        & obj.ItemPath        & """" ' Path
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LabelOrName: """     & obj.LabelOrName     & """" ' Name

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassKind: "     & CStr(obj.MetaClassKind   ) ' Metaclass Kind
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassName: """   & obj.MetaClassName   & """" ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "QualifiedName: """   & obj.QualifiedName   & """" ' Qualified Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AvailabilityContext: " & CStrObj(obj.AvailabilityContext) ' Availability Context
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Label: """           & obj.Label           & """" ' Label
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationClassKind: " & CStr(obj.DestinationClassKind) ' Target Kind
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationStereotype: """ & obj.DestinationStereotype & """" ' Target Stereotype

      End If
   Else

   End If

   DescribePdCommonExtendedCollectionTargetItem = Desc

Function DescribePdCommonEventHandlerTargetItem(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Event Handler

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Type: "              & CStr(obj.Type            ) ' Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ItemPath: """        & obj.ItemPath        & """" ' Path
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LabelOrName: """     & obj.LabelOrName     & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Target: "            & CStrObj(obj.Target       ) ' Target
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassKind: "     & CStr(obj.MetaClassKind   ) ' Metaclass Kind
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassName: """   & obj.MetaClassName   & """" ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "QualifiedName: """   & obj.QualifiedName   & """" ' Qualified Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AvailabilityContext: " & CStrObj(obj.AvailabilityContext) ' Availability Context
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "EventHandlerFunctionName: """ & obj.EventHandlerFunctionName & """" ' Functions Base Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GlobalScript: """    & obj.GlobalScript    & """" ' Global Script
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "HandlerScript: """   & obj.HandlerScript   & """" ' Event Handler Script
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonEventHandlerTargetItem = Desc

End Function

      End If
   Else

   End If

   DescribePdCommonTransformationTargetItem = Desc

Function DescribePdCommonUserProfile(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon User Profile

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Family: """          & obj.Family          & """" ' Family
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubFamily: """       & obj.SubFamily       & """" ' Subfamily
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExcludedDiagrams: """ & obj.ExcludedDiagrams & """" ' Excluded Diagrams
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LibraryID: """       & obj.LibraryID       & """" ' Type Library
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "HasExtendedMetaClass: " & CStr(obj.HasExtendedMetaClass) ' Has Extended MetaClass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RepositoryInformation: """ & obj.RepositoryInformation & """" ' Repository Information
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UpToDateStatus: "    & CStr(obj.UpToDateStatus  ) ' Up To Date Status
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RepositoryID: """    & obj.RepositoryID    & """" ' Repository Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtractionVersionID: " & CStr(obj.ExtractionVersionID) ' Model Extraction Version Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtractionVersion: """ & obj.ExtractionVersion & """" ' Model Extraction Version
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtractionBranchID: " & CStr(obj.ExtractionBranchID) ' Model Extraction Branch Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtractionDate: "    & CStr(obj.ExtractionDate  ) ' Model Extraction Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtractionEndDate: " & CStr(obj.ExtractionEndDate) ' Model Extraction End Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ApplicationVersion: """ & obj.ApplicationVersion & """" ' Application Version
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Filename: """        & obj.Filename        & """" ' File
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonUserProfile = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BrushStyle: "        & CStr(obj.BrushStyle      ) ' Brush Style

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AutoAdjustToText: "  & CStr(obj.AutoAdjustToText) ' Auto Adjust to Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ManuallyResized: "   & CStr(obj.ManuallyResized ) ' Resized
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepAspect: "        & CStr(obj.KeepAspect      ) ' Keep Aspect Ratio
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepCenter: "        & CStr(obj.KeepCenter      ) ' Keep Center
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepSize: "          & CStr(obj.KeepSize        ) ' Keep Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureType: " & CStr(obj.CustomPictureType) ' Custom Picture Type

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomShapeType: "   & CStr(obj.CustomShapeType ) ' Custom Shape Type

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubObjects: """      & obj.SubObjects      & """" ' Sub-objects Blob
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconMode: "          & CStr(obj.IconMode        ) ' Icon Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolContent: """   & obj.SymbolContent   & """" ' Symbol Content
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubSymbolsLayout: """ & obj.SubSymbolsLayout & """" ' Sub-Symbols Layout
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonDiagramSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCommonFileObjectSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon File Symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BrushStyle: "        & CStr(obj.BrushStyle      ) ' Brush Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientFillMode: "  & CStr(obj.GradientFillMode) ' Gradient Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientEndColor: "  & CStr(obj.GradientEndColor) ' Gradient End Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PictureFillMode: "   & CStr(obj.PictureFillMode ) ' Picture Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AutoAdjustToText: "  & CStr(obj.AutoAdjustToText) ' Auto Adjust to Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ManuallyResized: "   & CStr(obj.ManuallyResized ) ' Resized
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepAspect: "        & CStr(obj.KeepAspect      ) ' Keep Aspect Ratio
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepCenter: "        & CStr(obj.KeepCenter      ) ' Keep Center
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepSize: "          & CStr(obj.KeepSize        ) ' Keep Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureType: " & CStr(obj.CustomPictureType) ' Custom Picture Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomTextMode: "    & CStr(obj.CustomTextMode  ) ' Custom Picture Text Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureID: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureID & """" ' Background Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureID: """ & obj.CustomPictureID & """" ' Custom Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureFile: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureFile & """" ' Background Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureFile: """ & obj.CustomPictureFile & """" ' Custom Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomShapeType: "   & CStr(obj.CustomShapeType ) ' Custom Shape Type

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubObjects: """      & obj.SubObjects      & """" ' Sub-objects Blob
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconMode: "          & CStr(obj.IconMode        ) ' Icon Mode

      End If

   End If

   DescribePdCommonFileObjectSymbol = Desc

      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfPoints: "      & obj.ListOfPoints.AsText     ' List Points
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CornerStyle: "       & CStr(obj.CornerStyle     ) ' Corner Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ArrowStyle: "        & CStr(obj.ArrowStyle      ) ' Arrows
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkPosition: "      & obj.LinkPosition.AsText     ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkSize: "          & obj.LinkSize.AsText         ' Size

      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonNoteLinkSymbol = Desc

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconMode: "          & CStr(obj.IconMode        ) ' Icon Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolContent: """   & obj.SymbolContent   & """" ' Symbol Content
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubSymbolsLayout: """ & obj.SubSymbolsLayout & """" ' Sub-Symbols Layout
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonExtendedObjectSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCommonExtendedLinkSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Extended Link Symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfPoints: "      & obj.ListOfPoints.AsText     ' List Points
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CornerStyle: "       & CStr(obj.CornerStyle     ) ' Corner Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ArrowStyle: "        & CStr(obj.ArrowStyle      ) ' Arrows
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkPosition: "      & obj.LinkPosition.AsText     ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkSize: "          & obj.LinkSize.AsText         ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceSymbol: "      & CStrObj(obj.SourceSymbol ) ' Source Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationSymbol: " & CStrObj(obj.DestinationSymbol) ' Destination Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CenterTextOffset: "  & obj.CenterTextOffset.AsText ' Centered Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceTextOffset: "  & obj.SourceTextOffset.AsText ' Source Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationTextOffset: " & obj.DestinationTextOffset.AsText ' Destination Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FontList: """        & obj.FontList        & """" ' Font List
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object: "            & CStrObj(obj.Object       ) ' Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolContent: """   & obj.SymbolContent   & """" ' Symbol Content
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubSymbolsLayout: """ & obj.SubSymbolsLayout & """" ' Sub-Symbols Layout
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonExtendedLinkSymbol = Desc

End Function

' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Temporary internal object

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CheckName: """       & obj.CheckName       & """" ' Check
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectDescription: """ & obj.ObjectDescription & """" ' Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Check: "             & CStrObj(obj.Check        ) ' Check
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CheckObject: "       & CStrObj(obj.CheckObject  ) ' Check
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Severity: "          & CStr(obj.Severity        ) ' Severity

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Fixed: "             & CStr(obj.Fixed           ) ' Fixed

      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonCheckModelInternalMessage = Desc

End Function

Function DescribePdCommonDefaultDataSource(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Data Source

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview

      End If
   Else

   End If

   DescribePdCommonDefaultDataSource = Desc

End Function

Function DescribePdCommonDefaultStructuralFeatureMapping(obj)

      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date

   Else

   End If

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubFamily: """       & obj.SubFamily       & """" ' Sub family

      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

End Function

      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDateInRepository: " & CStr(obj.CreationDateInRepository) ' Creation Date in Repository
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDateInRepository: " & CStr(obj.ModificationDateInRepository) ' Modification Date in Repository
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectIdentifier: "  & CStr(obj.ObjectIdentifier) ' Object Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Connection: "        & CStrObj(obj.Connection   ) ' Connection
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassID: """         & obj.ClassID         & """" ' Class Globally Unique Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKindInRepository: " & CStr(obj.ClassKindInRepository) ' Stored Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectStatus: "      & CStr(obj.ObjectStatus    ) ' Object Status (locked, ...)
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Location: """        & obj.Location        & """" ' Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PermanentID: "       & CStr(obj.PermanentID     ) ' Permanent Object Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Frozen: "            & CStr(obj.Frozen          ) ' Frozen
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Version: """         & obj.Version         & """" ' Version
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "XClssID: "           & CStr(obj.XClssID         ) ' Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IsProject: "         & CStr(obj.IsProject       ) ' Is Project
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ProjectModel: "      & CStrObj(obj.ProjectModel ) ' Project Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ParentProject: "     & CStrObj(obj.ParentProject) ' Parent Project
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdRMGRepositoryFolder = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdRMGRepositoryConnection(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdRMG Repository Connection

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDateInRepository: " & CStr(obj.CreationDateInRepository) ' Creation Date in Repository
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDateInRepository: " & CStr(obj.ModificationDateInRepository) ' Modification Date in Repository
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectIdentifier: "  & CStr(obj.ObjectIdentifier) ' Object Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Connection: "        & CStrObj(obj.Connection   ) ' Connection
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassID: """         & obj.ClassID         & """" ' Class Globally Unique Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKindInRepository: " & CStr(obj.ClassKindInRepository) ' Stored Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectStatus: "      & CStr(obj.ObjectStatus    ) ' Object Status (locked, ...)
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Location: """        & obj.Location        & """" ' Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PermanentID: "       & CStr(obj.PermanentID     ) ' Permanent Object Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Frozen: "            & CStr(obj.Frozen          ) ' Frozen
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Version: """         & obj.Version         & """" ' Version
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "XClssID: "           & CStr(obj.XClssID         ) ' Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IsProject: "         & CStr(obj.IsProject       ) ' Is Project
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ProjectModel: "      & CStrObj(obj.ProjectModel ) ' Project Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ParentProject: "     & CStrObj(obj.ParentProject) ' Parent Project
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Connected: "         & CStr(obj.Connected       ) ' Connected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RepositoryDefinitionName: """ & obj.RepositoryDefinitionName & """" ' Repository Definition Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CurrentBranchName: """ & obj.CurrentBranchName & """" ' Current Branch Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LDAPTrusted: "       & CStr(obj.LDAPTrusted     ) ' LDAP Trusted Server
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LDAPProvider: """    & obj.LDAPProvider    & """" ' LDAP Provider URL
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LDAPSecurity: """    & obj.LDAPSecurity    & """" ' LDAP Security Protocol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LDAPDefaultBase: """ & obj.LDAPDefaultBase & """" ' LDAP Default Search Base
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LDAPServerType: """  & obj.LDAPServerType  & """" ' LDAP Server Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LDAPAnonymousBind: " & CStr(obj.LDAPAnonymousBind) ' LDAP Anonymous Bind
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LDAPBindDN: """      & obj.LDAPBindDN      & """" ' LDAP Bind DN
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LDAPBindPassword: """ & obj.LDAPBindPassword & """" ' LDAP Bind Password
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LDAPAuthorizationFilter: """ & obj.LDAPAuthorizationFilter & """" ' LDAP Authentication Filter
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LDAPAuthorizationScope: """ & obj.LDAPAuthorizationScope & """" ' LDAP Authentication Scope
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LDAPAuthorizationMethod: """ & obj.LDAPAuthorizationMethod & """" ' LDAP Authentication Method
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LDAPAuthorizationDigest: """ & obj.LDAPAuthorizationDigest & """" ' LDAP Digest Format
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LDAPAuthorizationBase: """ & obj.LDAPAuthorizationBase & """" ' LDAP Authentication Search Base
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LDAPRoleFilter: """  & obj.LDAPRoleFilter  & """" ' LDAP Role Filter
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LDAPRoleScope: """   & obj.LDAPRoleScope   & """" ' LDAP Role Scope
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LDAPRoleReferral: """ & obj.LDAPRoleReferral & """" ' LDAP Role Referral
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LDAPRoleName: """    & obj.LDAPRoleName    & """" ' LDAP Role Name Attribute
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LDAPRoleBase: """    & obj.LDAPRoleBase    & """" ' LDAP Role Search Base
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdRMGRepositoryConnection = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdRMGRepositoryDocument(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdRMG Document

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDateInRepository: " & CStr(obj.CreationDateInRepository) ' Creation Date in Repository
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDateInRepository: " & CStr(obj.ModificationDateInRepository) ' Modification Date in Repository
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectIdentifier: "  & CStr(obj.ObjectIdentifier) ' Object Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Connection: "        & CStrObj(obj.Connection   ) ' Connection
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassID: """         & obj.ClassID         & """" ' Class Globally Unique Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKindInRepository: " & CStr(obj.ClassKindInRepository) ' Stored Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectStatus: "      & CStr(obj.ObjectStatus    ) ' Object Status (locked, ...)
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Location: """        & obj.Location        & """" ' Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PermanentID: "       & CStr(obj.PermanentID     ) ' Permanent Object Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Frozen: "            & CStr(obj.Frozen          ) ' Frozen
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Version: """         & obj.Version         & """" ' Version
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "XClssID: "           & CStr(obj.XClssID         ) ' Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "VersionComment: """  & obj.VersionComment  & """" ' Version Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtractionName: """  & obj.ExtractionName  & """" ' Default Check Out File Name
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdRMGRepositoryDocument = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectIdentifier: "  & CStr(obj.ObjectIdentifier) ' Object Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Connection: "        & CStrObj(obj.Connection   ) ' Connection
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassID: """         & obj.ClassID         & """" ' Class Globally Unique Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKindInRepository: " & CStr(obj.ClassKindInRepository) ' Stored Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectStatus: "      & CStr(obj.ObjectStatus    ) ' Object Status (locked, ...)
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Location: """        & obj.Location        & """" ' Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PermanentID: "       & CStr(obj.PermanentID     ) ' Permanent Object Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Frozen: "            & CStr(obj.Frozen          ) ' Frozen
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Version: """         & obj.Version         & """" ' Version
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "XClssID: "           & CStr(obj.XClssID         ) ' Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdRMGRepositoryObject = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedMetaclassID: " & CStr(obj.ExtendedMetaclassID) ' Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BaseMetaclassID: "   & CStr(obj.BaseMetaclassID ) ' Base metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Plural: """          & obj.Plural          & """" ' Plural
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flags
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Icon: "              & CStr(obj.Icon            ) ' Icon
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdRMGRepositoryExtendedMetaclass = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BrushStyle: "        & CStr(obj.BrushStyle      ) ' Brush Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientFillMode: "  & CStr(obj.GradientFillMode) ' Gradient Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientEndColor: "  & CStr(obj.GradientEndColor) ' Gradient End Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PictureFillMode: "   & CStr(obj.PictureFillMode ) ' Picture Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AutoAdjustToText: "  & CStr(obj.AutoAdjustToText) ' Auto Adjust to Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ManuallyResized: "   & CStr(obj.ManuallyResized ) ' Resized
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepAspect: "        & CStr(obj.KeepAspect      ) ' Keep Aspect Ratio
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepCenter: "        & CStr(obj.KeepCenter      ) ' Keep Center
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepSize: "          & CStr(obj.KeepSize        ) ' Keep Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureType: " & CStr(obj.CustomPictureType) ' Custom Picture Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomTextMode: "    & CStr(obj.CustomTextMode  ) ' Custom Picture Text Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureID: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureID & """" ' Background Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureID: """ & obj.CustomPictureID & """" ' Custom Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureFile: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureFile & """" ' Background Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureFile: """ & obj.CustomPictureFile & """" ' Custom Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomShapeType: "   & CStr(obj.CustomShapeType ) ' Custom Shape Type

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object: "            & CStrObj(obj.Object       ) ' Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubObjects: """      & obj.SubObjects      & """" ' Sub-objects Blob
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconMode: "          & CStr(obj.IconMode        ) ' Icon Mode

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubSymbolsLayout: """ & obj.SubSymbolsLayout & """" ' Sub-Symbols Layout
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCommonEndSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCommonBaseOrgnSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Organization Unit symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else

Function DescribePdCommonTransitionSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCommon Transition symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfPoints: "      & obj.ListOfPoints.AsText     ' List Points

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkSize: "          & obj.LinkSize.AsText         ' Size

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationSymbol: " & CStrObj(obj.DestinationSymbol) ' Destination Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CenterTextOffset: "  & obj.CenterTextOffset.AsText ' Centered Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceTextOffset: "  & obj.SourceTextOffset.AsText ' Source Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationTextOffset: " & obj.DestinationTextOffset.AsText ' Destination Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FontList: """        & obj.FontList        & """" ' Font List

      End If
   Else

   End If

Function DescribePdPDMTable(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Table

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultMapping: "    & CStrObj(obj.DefaultMapping) ' Mapping
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DBMS: "              & CStrObj(obj.DBMS         ) ' DBMS
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolDisplayed: "   & CStr(obj.SymbolDisplayed ) ' Has Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClusterObject: "     & CStrObj(obj.ClusterObject) ' Cluster
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "XMLElementObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.XMLElementObject) ' Element
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GeneratedName: """   & obj.GeneratedName   & """" ' Generated Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "QualifiedCode: """   & obj.QualifiedCode   & """" ' Qualified Code

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Type: """            & obj.Type            & """" ' Type

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClientCheckExpression: """ & obj.ClientCheckExpression & """" ' Client Validation Rule

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CheckConstraintName: """ & obj.CheckConstraintName & """" ' Check Constraint Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StartDate: "         & CStr(obj.StartDate       ) ' Start date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PartitionRange: "    & CStr(obj.PartitionRange  ) ' Partition range
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PartitionRangeUnit: " & CStr(obj.PartitionRangeUnit) ' Partition range time unit
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RowGrowthRate: "     & CStr(obj.RowGrowthRate   ) ' Row growth rate
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "InitialRows: "       & CStr(obj.InitialRows     ) ' Initial rows
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TotalSaving: "       & CStr(obj.TotalSaving     ) ' Total saving
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TotalSavingPercentage: " & CStr(obj.TotalSavingPercentage) ' Total saving percentage
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TotalSavingCurrency: """ & obj.TotalSavingCurrency & """" ' Currency
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Lifecycle: "         & CStrObj(obj.Lifecycle    ) ' Lifecycle
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMTable = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdPDMColumn(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Column

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview

End Function 

Function DescribePdPDMIndex(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Index

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DBMS: "              & CStrObj(obj.DBMS         ) ' DBMS
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Table: "             & CStrObj(obj.Table        ) ' Table
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Owner: "             & CStrObj(obj.Owner        ) ' Owner
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "QualifiedCode: """   & obj.QualifiedCode   & """" ' Qualified Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FullyQualifiedCode: """ & obj.FullyQualifiedCode & """" ' Fully Qualified Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Indicator: """       & obj.Indicator       & """" ' Indicator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PhysicalOptions: """ & obj.PhysicalOptions & """" ' Options
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Type: """            & obj.Type            & """" ' Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Unique: "            & CStr(obj.Unique          ) ' Unique
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Clustered: "         & CStr(obj.Clustered       ) ' Cluster
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Primary: "           & CStr(obj.Primary         ) ' Primary
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ForeignKey: "        & CStr(obj.ForeignKey      ) ' Foreign Key
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AlternateKey: "      & CStr(obj.AlternateKey    ) ' Alternate Key
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkedObject: "      & CStrObj(obj.LinkedObject ) ' Linked Object
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMIndex = Desc

End Function

Function DescribePdPDMJoinIndexReference(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Join Index Reference

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
