      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMJoinIndexReference = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdPDMKey(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Key

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DBMS: "              & CStrObj(obj.DBMS         ) ' DBMS
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Table: "             & CStrObj(obj.Table        ) ' Table
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Indicator: """       & obj.Indicator       & """" ' Indicator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Primary: "           & CStr(obj.Primary         ) ' Primary
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Clustered: "         & CStr(obj.Clustered       ) ' Cluster
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PhysicalOptions: """ & obj.PhysicalOptions & """" ' Options
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ConstraintName: """  & obj.ConstraintName  & """" ' Constraint Name
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMKey = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdPDMReference(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Reference

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object2: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object2      ) ' Second Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object1: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object1      ) ' First Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultMapping: "    & CStrObj(obj.DefaultMapping) ' Mapping
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DBMS: "              & CStrObj(obj.DBMS         ) ' DBMS
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ParentTable: "       & CStrObj(obj.ParentTable  ) ' Parent Table
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ChildTable: "        & CStrObj(obj.ChildTable   ) ' Child Table
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ParentKey: "         & CStrObj(obj.ParentKey    ) ' Parent Key
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Primary: "           & CStr(obj.Primary         ) ' Primary
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MinimumCardinality: """ & obj.MinimumCardinality & """" ' Minimum Cardinality
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MaximumCardinality: """ & obj.MaximumCardinality & """" ' Maximum Cardinality

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ForeignKeyColumnList: """ & obj.ForeignKeyColumnList & """" ' Foreign Key Columns

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ChildRole: """       & obj.ChildRole       & """" ' Child Role
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ChangeParentAllowed: " & CStr(obj.ChangeParentAllowed) ' Change Parent Allowed

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Idef1xCardinality: """ & obj.Idef1xCardinality & """" ' IDEF1X Cardinality
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Cardinality: """     & obj.Cardinality     & """" ' Cardinality
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UpdateConstraint: "  & CStr(obj.UpdateConstraint) ' Update Constraint
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DeleteConstraint: "  & CStr(obj.DeleteConstraint) ' Delete Constraint
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ImplementationType: """ & obj.ImplementationType & """" ' Implementation
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMReference = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype

   Else

   End If

End Function

   Else

   End If

End Function 

Function DescribePdPDMProcedure(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Procedure

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DBMS: "              & CStrObj(obj.DBMS         ) ' DBMS
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Owner: "             & CStrObj(obj.Owner        ) ' Owner
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TextPreview: """     & obj.TextPreview     & """" ' SQL Query
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Table: "             & CStrObj(obj.Table        ) ' Table
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolDisplayed: "   & CStr(obj.SymbolDisplayed ) ' Has Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OwnerDisplayName: """ & obj.OwnerDisplayName & """" ' Owner and Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "QualifiedCode: """   & obj.QualifiedCode   & """" ' Qualified Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FullyQualifiedCode: """ & obj.FullyQualifiedCode & """" ' Fully Qualified Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ProcedureTemplate: " & CStrObj(obj.ProcedureTemplate) ' Procedure Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Method: "            & CStrObj(obj.Method       ) ' Method
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ImplementationType: """ & obj.ImplementationType & """" ' Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Text: """            & obj.Text            & """" ' Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BeginScript: """     & obj.BeginScript     & """" ' Begin Script
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "EndScript: """       & obj.EndScript       & """" ' End Script
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MethodName: """      & obj.MethodName      & """" ' Method
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Function: "          & CStr(obj.Function        ) ' Type
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMProcedure = Desc

End Function

Function DescribePdPDMProcedureTemplate(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Procedure Template

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DBMS: "              & CStrObj(obj.DBMS         ) ' DBMS
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Function: "          & CStr(obj.Function        ) ' Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Text: """            & obj.Text            & """" ' Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ProcedureName: """   & obj.ProcedureName   & """" ' Procedure Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TablLinked: "        & CStr(obj.TablLinked      ) ' Linked to Table
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ImplementationType: """ & obj.ImplementationType & """" ' Type
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMProcedureTemplate = Desc

End Function

Function DescribePdPDMSequence(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Sequence

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation

End Function 

Function DescribePdPDMPhysicalDomain(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Domain

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Unit: """            & obj.Unit            & """" ' Unit
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Format: """          & obj.Format          & """" ' Format
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LowValue: """        & obj.LowValue        & """" ' Minimum Value
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "HighValue: """       & obj.HighValue       & """" ' Maximum Value
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultValue: """    & obj.DefaultValue    & """" ' Default Value
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Uppercase: "         & CStr(obj.Uppercase       ) ' Uppercase
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Lowercase: "         & CStr(obj.Lowercase       ) ' Lowercase
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CannotModify: "      & CStr(obj.CannotModify    ) ' Cannot Modify
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfValues: """    & obj.ListOfValues    & """" ' List of Values
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClientCheckExpression: """ & obj.ClientCheckExpression & """" ' Client Validation Rule
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ServerCheckExpression: """ & obj.ServerCheckExpression & """" ' Server Validation Rule
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Complete: "          & CStr(obj.Complete        ) ' Complete
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "NoSpace: "           & CStr(obj.NoSpace         ) ' No space
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CharacterCase: "     & CStr(obj.CharacterCase   ) ' Case
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FormatObject: "      & CStrObj(obj.FormatObject ) ' Format object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultMapping: "    & CStrObj(obj.DefaultMapping) ' Mapping
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DataType: """        & obj.DataType        & """" ' Data Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Length: "            & CStr(obj.Length          ) ' Length
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Precision: "         & CStr(obj.Precision       ) ' Precision
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Mandatory: "         & CStr(obj.Mandatory       ) ' Mandatory
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DBMS: "              & CStrObj(obj.DBMS         ) ' DBMS
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TestDataProfile: "   & CStrObj(obj.TestDataProfile) ' Test Data Profile
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AbstractDataType: "  & CStrObj(obj.AbstractDataType) ' Abstract Data Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CheckExpressionPreview: """ & obj.CheckExpressionPreview & """" ' Check
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SerialDataType: "    & CStr(obj.SerialDataType  ) ' Serial Data Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Owner: "             & CStrObj(obj.Owner        ) ' Owner
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Default: "           & CStrObj(obj.Default      ) ' Default
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultValueDisplayed: """ & obj.DefaultValueDisplayed & """" ' Default
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfValuesWithoutLabel: """ & obj.ListOfValuesWithoutLabel & """" ' List of Values
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "QualifiedCode: """   & obj.QualifiedCode   & """" ' Qualified Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FullyQualifiedCode: """ & obj.FullyQualifiedCode & """" ' Fully Qualified Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ConceptualDataType: """ & obj.ConceptualDataType & """" ' Conceptual Data Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Identity: "          & CStr(obj.Identity        ) ' Identity
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "WithDefault: "       & CStr(obj.WithDefault     ) ' With Default
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMPhysicalDomain = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdPDMDatabase(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Database

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DBMS: "              & CStrObj(obj.DBMS         ) ' DBMS
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PhysicalOptions: """ & obj.PhysicalOptions & """" ' Options
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BeginScript: """     & obj.BeginScript     & """" ' Begin Script
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "EndScript: """       & obj.EndScript       & """" ' End Script
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMDatabase = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FileDSN: """         & obj.FileDSN         & """" ' Options

      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMBasePhysicalModelOptions = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdPDMDefaultPhysicalOptions(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Default Physical Options

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PhysicalOptions: """ & obj.PhysicalOptions & """" ' Options
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DBMS: "              & CStrObj(obj.DBMS         ) ' DBMS
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Generated: "         & CStr(obj.Generated       ) ' Generate
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DBMSPath: """        & obj.DBMSPath        & """" ' Generate
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Caption: """         & obj.Caption         & """" ' Generate
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Primary: "           & CStr(obj.Primary         ) ' Primary
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMDefaultPhysicalOptions = Desc

End Function

Function DescribePdPDMPhysicalOptionsItem(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Physical Option Item

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Type: "              & CStr(obj.Type            ) ' Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Order: "             & CStr(obj.Order           ) ' Order
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultValue: """    & obj.DefaultValue    & """" ' Default Value
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfValues: """    & obj.ListOfValues    & """" ' List of Values
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Value: """           & obj.Value           & """" ' Value
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CollectionString: """ & obj.CollectionString & """" ' Collection string
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ContentType: """     & obj.ContentType     & """" ' Content type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ContentStereotype: """ & obj.ContentStereotype & """" ' Content stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ContentStereotypeUseAsMetaclass: " & CStr(obj.ContentStereotypeUseAsMetaclass) ' Content stereotype use as metaclass
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMPhysicalOptionsItem = Desc

End Function

   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Fact: "              & CStrObj(obj.Fact         ) ' Fact
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultMapping: "    & CStrObj(obj.DefaultMapping) ' Default Mapping
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMCube = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdPDMCubeDimensionAssociation(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Association

   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then

      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass

   End If

' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Data Source

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DataSourceName: """  & obj.DataSourceName  & """" ' ODBC Data Source
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DataSourceLogin: """ & obj.DataSourceLogin & """" ' Login
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DataSourcePassword: """ & obj.DataSourcePassword & """" ' Password
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AccessType: """      & obj.AccessType      & """" ' Access Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModelType: "         & CStr(obj.ModelType       ) ' Model Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Cost: "              & CStr(obj.Cost            ) ' Cost (per GB)
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Currency: """        & obj.Currency        & """" ' Currency
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CompressionRate: "   & CStr(obj.CompressionRate ) ' Compression rate
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMDataSource = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdPDMTableMapping(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Table Mapping

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Criteria: """        & obj.Criteria        & """" ' Criteria
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Expression: """      & obj.Expression      & """" ' Expression
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SelectStatement: """ & obj.SelectStatement & """" ' Select
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "InsertStatement: """ & obj.InsertStatement & """" ' Insert
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UpdateStatement: """ & obj.UpdateStatement & """" ' Update
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DeleteStatement: """ & obj.DeleteStatement & """" ' Delete
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Classifier: "        & CStrObj(obj.Classifier   ) ' Classifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DataSource: "        & CStrObj(obj.DataSource   ) ' Data Source
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MappedTo: """        & obj.MappedTo        & """" ' Mapped to
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Reversible: "        & CStr(obj.Reversible      ) ' Reversible
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Select: """          & obj.Select          & """" ' Select
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Table: "             & CStrObj(obj.Table        ) ' Table
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMTableMapping = Desc

End Function

   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Criteria: """        & obj.Criteria        & """" ' Criteria
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Expression: """      & obj.Expression      & """" ' Expression
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SelectStatement: """ & obj.SelectStatement & """" ' Select
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "InsertStatement: """ & obj.InsertStatement & """" ' Insert
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UpdateStatement: """ & obj.UpdateStatement & """" ' Update
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DeleteStatement: """ & obj.DeleteStatement & """" ' Delete

Function DescribePdPDMCubeMapping(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Cube Mapping

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent

   End If

   DescribePdPDMSynonym = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdPDMDatabasePackage(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Database Package

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Generated: "         & CStr(obj.Generated       ) ' Generate
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Initialization: """  & obj.Initialization  & """" ' Initialization
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Authorization: """   & obj.Authorization   & """" ' Authorization
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UserDefined: "       & CStr(obj.UserDefined     ) ' User-Defined
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DBMS: "              & CStrObj(obj.DBMS         ) ' DBMS
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Owner: "             & CStrObj(obj.Owner        ) ' Owner
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "QualifiedCode: """   & obj.QualifiedCode   & """" ' Qualified Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FullyQualifiedCode: """ & obj.FullyQualifiedCode & """" ' Fully Qualified Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Template: "          & CStrObj(obj.Template     ) ' Database Package Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Table: "             & CStrObj(obj.Table        ) ' Table
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMDatabasePackage = Desc

End Function

' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Database Package Exception

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name

   Else

   End If

Function DescribePdPDMDatabasePackageProcedure(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Database Package Procedure

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview

   Else

   End If

Function DescribePdPDMPermission(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Permission

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object1: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object1      ) ' First Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkedObject: "      & CStrObj(obj.LinkedObject ) ' Linked Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Grant: """           & obj.Grant           & """" ' Grant
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GrantWithOption: """ & obj.GrantWithOption & """" ' Grant With Option
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Revoke: """          & obj.Revoke          & """" ' Revoke
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RevokeWithCascade: """ & obj.RevokeWithCascade & """" ' Revoke With Cascade

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DBObject: "          & CStrObj(obj.DBObject     ) ' Object
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMPermission = Desc

End Function

   Else

   End If

   DescribePdPDMPartition = Desc

Function DescribePdPDMHorizontalPartitioning(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Horizontal Partitioning

   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then

      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMWebService = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdPDMWebOperation(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Web Operation

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DBMS: "              & CStrObj(obj.DBMS         ) ' DBMS
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FullPath: """        & obj.FullPath        & """" ' Full Path
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Implementation: """  & obj.Implementation  & """" ' Implementation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ImplementationPreview: """ & obj.ImplementationPreview & """" ' Implementation Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OperationType: """   & obj.OperationType   & """" ' Operation Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "WebService: "        & CStrObj(obj.WebService   ) ' Service
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Prototype: """       & obj.Prototype       & """" ' Prototype

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AuthorizationRequired: " & CStr(obj.AuthorizationRequired) ' Required Authorization

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Owner: "             & CStrObj(obj.Owner        ) ' Owner
      End If
   Else

   End If

   DescribePdPDMWebOperation = Desc

End Function

' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Lifecycle

   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then

         Desc = "<Nothing>"

Function DescribePdPDMPhase(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Phase

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "EnableShortcutOfFlow: " & CStr(obj.EnableShortcutOfFlow) ' Enable Shortcut Of Flow
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdBPMBusinessProcessModelOptions = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdBPMPackageOptions(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdBPM Package Options

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationCheckModel: " & CStr(obj.GenerationCheckModel) ' Generation Check Model Before
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationPath: """  & obj.GenerationPath  & """" ' Generation Path Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOptionsBLOB: """ & obj.GenerationOptionsBLOB & """" ' Generation Options
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationCommandsBLOB: """ & obj.GenerationCommandsBLOB & """" ' Generation Commands
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationTargetsBLOB: """ & obj.GenerationTargetsBLOB & """" ' Generation Targets
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SelectedSettingsBlob: """ & obj.SelectedSettingsBlob & """" ' Selected Settings
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SelectedSelectionBlob: """ & obj.SelectedSelectionBlob & """" ' Current Selection
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CheckSubPackages: "  & CStr(obj.CheckSubPackages) ' Check Subfolders

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ReverseCreateXML: "  & CStr(obj.ReverseCreateXML) ' Create XML Model
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdBPMPackageOptions = Desc

End Function

      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageMargins: "       & obj.PageMargins.AsText      ' Page Margins
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageFormat: "        & CStr(obj.PageFormat      ) ' Page Format

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SwimlaneHeaderHeight: " & CStr(obj.SwimlaneHeaderHeight) ' Swimlane Header Height

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History

   End If

         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
