         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CompositeLocation: """ & obj.CompositeLocation & """" ' Process Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SentFaultMessage: "  & CStrObj(obj.SentFaultMessage) ' Sent fault
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ReceptionCorrelation: " & CStrObj(obj.ReceptionCorrelation) ' Input Correlation Key
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "EmissionCorrelation: " & CStrObj(obj.EmissionCorrelation) ' Output Correlation Key
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdBPMProcess = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdBPMMessageFormat(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdBPM Message Format

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Type: """            & obj.Type            & """" ' Message Format Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Definition: """      & obj.Definition      & """" ' Message Format Definition
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Location: """        & obj.Location        & """" ' External Definition
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefinitionType: "    & CStr(obj.DefinitionType  ) ' Definition Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ServiceProvider: "   & CStrObj(obj.ServiceProvider) ' Service Provider
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "XMLModel: "          & CStrObj(obj.XMLModel     ) ' XSD Model
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdBPMMessageFormat = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdBPMMessagePart(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdBPM Message Part

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview

      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdBPMMessagePart = Desc

End Function

      End If
   Else

   End If

   DescribePdBPMDecision = Desc

      End If
   Else

   End If

Function DescribePdBPMOperation(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdBPM Operation

      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica

Function DescribePdBPMFaultMessage(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdBPM Fault

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object1: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object1      ) ' First Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkedObject: "      & CStrObj(obj.LinkedObject ) ' Linked Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OperationName: """   & obj.OperationName   & """" ' Operation Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OperationCode: """   & obj.OperationCode   & """" ' Operation Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OperationType: "     & CStr(obj.OperationType   ) ' Operation Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OperationInterface: " & CStrObj(obj.OperationInterface) ' Operation Interface
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MessageFormatName: """ & obj.MessageFormatName & """" ' Message Format Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MessageFormatCode: """ & obj.MessageFormatCode & """" ' Message Format Code

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MessageFormatDefinition: """ & obj.MessageFormatDefinition & """" ' Message Format Definition
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MessageFormatLocation: """ & obj.MessageFormatLocation & """" ' Message Format Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MessageFormatLocationType: " & CStr(obj.MessageFormatLocationType) ' Message Format Location Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Operation: "         & CStrObj(obj.Operation    ) ' Operation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MessageFormat: "     & CStrObj(obj.MessageFormat) ' Message Format
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Fault: """           & obj.Fault           & """" ' Fault
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdBPMFaultMessage = Desc

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ReadAccess: "        & CStr(obj.ReadAccess      ) ' Read Access
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UpdateAccess: "      & CStr(obj.UpdateAccess    ) ' Update Access
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DeleteAccess: "      & CStr(obj.DeleteAccess    ) ' Delete Access
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Process: "           & CStrObj(obj.Process      ) ' Process
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Resource: "          & CStrObj(obj.Resource     ) ' Resource
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CRUD: "              & CStr(obj.CRUD            ) ' CRUD
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdBPMResourceFlow = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdBPMProcessStart(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdBPM Start

   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtractionEndDate: " & CStr(obj.ExtractionEndDate) ' Model Extraction End Date

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Filename: """        & obj.Filename        & """" ' File
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdBPMProcessLanguage = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdBPMVariable(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdBPM Variable

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DataType: """        & obj.DataType        & """" ' Data Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Constant: "          & CStr(obj.Constant        ) ' Constant
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Value: """           & obj.Value           & """" ' Value
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ElementType: "       & CStr(obj.ElementType     ) ' Element type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DataTypeObject: "    & CStrObj(obj.DataTypeObject) ' Data Type Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "InputParameter: "    & CStr(obj.InputParameter  ) ' Input Parameter
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OutputParameter: "   & CStr(obj.OutputParameter ) ' Output Parameter
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdBPMVariable = Desc

End Function

      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "EventType: "         & CStr(obj.EventType       ) ' Event Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DeadlineTimer: "     & CStr(obj.DeadlineTimer   ) ' Deadline Timer
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TimerExpression: """ & obj.TimerExpression & """" ' Timer Expression
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdBPMEvent = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdBPMRoleAssociation(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdBPM Role Association

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object2: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object2      ) ' Second Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object1: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object1      ) ' First Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Source: "            & CStrObj(obj.Source       ) ' Source
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Destination: "       & CStrObj(obj.Destination  ) ' Destination
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "InitiatingRole: "    & CStr(obj.InitiatingRole  ) ' Initiating Role
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdBPMRoleAssociation = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CompositeView: "     & CStr(obj.CompositeView   ) ' Composite View
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdBPMProcessSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdBPMDecisionSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdBPM Decision symbol

   Dim Desc

      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfPoints: "      & obj.ListOfPoints.AsText     ' List Points
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CornerStyle: "       & CStr(obj.CornerStyle     ) ' Corner Style

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkSize: "          & obj.LinkSize.AsText         ' Size

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object: "            & CStrObj(obj.Object       ) ' Object

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubSymbolsLayout: """ & obj.SubSymbolsLayout & """" ' Sub-Symbols Layout
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdBPMFlowSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdBPMFormatSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdBPM Message Format symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BrushStyle: "        & CStr(obj.BrushStyle      ) ' Brush Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientFillMode: "  & CStr(obj.GradientFillMode) ' Gradient Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientEndColor: "  & CStr(obj.GradientEndColor) ' Gradient End Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PictureFillMode: "   & CStr(obj.PictureFillMode ) ' Picture Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AutoAdjustToText: "  & CStr(obj.AutoAdjustToText) ' Auto Adjust to Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ManuallyResized: "   & CStr(obj.ManuallyResized ) ' Resized
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepAspect: "        & CStr(obj.KeepAspect      ) ' Keep Aspect Ratio
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepCenter: "        & CStr(obj.KeepCenter      ) ' Keep Center
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepSize: "          & CStr(obj.KeepSize        ) ' Keep Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureType: " & CStr(obj.CustomPictureType) ' Custom Picture Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomTextMode: "    & CStr(obj.CustomTextMode  ) ' Custom Picture Text Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureID: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureID & """" ' Background Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureID: """ & obj.CustomPictureID & """" ' Custom Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureFile: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureFile & """" ' Background Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureFile: """ & obj.CustomPictureFile & """" ' Custom Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomShapeType: "   & CStr(obj.CustomShapeType ) ' Custom Shape Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FontList: """        & obj.FontList        & """" ' Font List
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object: "            & CStrObj(obj.Object       ) ' Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubObjects: """      & obj.SubObjects      & """" ' Sub-objects Blob
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconMode: "          & CStr(obj.IconMode        ) ' Icon Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolContent: """   & obj.SymbolContent   & """" ' Symbol Content
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubSymbolsLayout: """ & obj.SubSymbolsLayout & """" ' Sub-Symbols Layout
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdBPMFormatSymbol = Desc

End Function

' Build a the full text description of a PdBPM Resource Flow Symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfPoints: "      & obj.ListOfPoints.AsText     ' List Points
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CornerStyle: "       & CStr(obj.CornerStyle     ) ' Corner Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ArrowStyle: "        & CStr(obj.ArrowStyle      ) ' Arrows
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkPosition: "      & obj.LinkPosition.AsText     ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkSize: "          & obj.LinkSize.AsText         ' Size

   End If

   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then

      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BrushStyle: "        & CStr(obj.BrushStyle      ) ' Brush Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientFillMode: "  & CStr(obj.GradientFillMode) ' Gradient Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientEndColor: "  & CStr(obj.GradientEndColor) ' Gradient End Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PictureFillMode: "   & CStr(obj.PictureFillMode ) ' Picture Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AutoAdjustToText: "  & CStr(obj.AutoAdjustToText) ' Auto Adjust to Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ManuallyResized: "   & CStr(obj.ManuallyResized ) ' Resized

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepCenter: "        & CStr(obj.KeepCenter      ) ' Keep Center

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureID: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureID & """" ' Background Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureID: """ & obj.CustomPictureID & """" ' Custom Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureFile: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureFile & """" ' Background Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureFile: """ & obj.CustomPictureFile & """" ' Custom Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomShapeType: "   & CStr(obj.CustomShapeType ) ' Custom Shape Type

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubObjects: """      & obj.SubObjects      & """" ' Sub-objects Blob
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconMode: "          & CStr(obj.IconMode        ) ' Icon Mode

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubSymbolsLayout: """ & obj.SubSymbolsLayout & """" ' Sub-Symbols Layout
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CompositeView: "     & CStr(obj.CompositeView   ) ' Composite View
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdBPMConversationNodeSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdBPMConversationLinkSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdBPM Conversation Link Symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfPoints: "      & obj.ListOfPoints.AsText     ' List Points
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CornerStyle: "       & CStr(obj.CornerStyle     ) ' Corner Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ArrowStyle: "        & CStr(obj.ArrowStyle      ) ' Arrows
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkPosition: "      & obj.LinkPosition.AsText     ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkSize: "          & obj.LinkSize.AsText         ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceSymbol: "      & CStrObj(obj.SourceSymbol ) ' Source Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationSymbol: " & CStrObj(obj.DestinationSymbol) ' Destination Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CenterTextOffset: "  & obj.CenterTextOffset.AsText ' Centered Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceTextOffset: "  & obj.SourceTextOffset.AsText ' Source Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationTextOffset: " & obj.DestinationTextOffset.AsText ' Destination Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FontList: """        & obj.FontList        & """" ' Font List
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object: "            & CStrObj(obj.Object       ) ' Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolContent: """   & obj.SymbolContent   & """" ' Symbol Content
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubSymbolsLayout: """ & obj.SubSymbolsLayout & """" ' Sub-Symbols Layout
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdBPMConversationLinkSymbol = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconMode: "          & CStr(obj.IconMode        ) ' Icon Mode

      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdBPMOrganizationUnitConversationDiagramSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCDMModel(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCDM Conceptual Data Model

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolDisplayed: "   & CStr(obj.SymbolDisplayed ) ' Has Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultDiagram: "    & CStrObj(obj.DefaultDiagram) ' Default Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModelOptionsText: """ & obj.ModelOptionsText & """" ' Model Options

   Else

   End If

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultMapping: "    & CStrObj(obj.DefaultMapping) ' Mapping
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolDisplayed: "   & CStr(obj.SymbolDisplayed ) ' Has Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Number: "            & CStr(obj.Number          ) ' Number
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Generated: "         & CStr(obj.Generated       ) ' Generate
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCDMAssociation = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCDMDataItem(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCDM Data Item

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent

      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultMapping: "    & CStrObj(obj.DefaultMapping) ' Mapping
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Entity1ToEntity2RoleMaximumCardinality: """ & obj.Entity1ToEntity2RoleMaximumCardinality & """" ' Entity 1 -> Entity 2 Role Max. Cardinality
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Entity1ToEntity2RoleMinimumCardinality: """ & obj.Entity1ToEntity2RoleMinimumCardinality & """" ' Entity 1 -> Entity 2 Role Min. Cardinality
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Entity2ToEntity1RoleMaximumCardinality: """ & obj.Entity2ToEntity1RoleMaximumCardinality & """" ' Entity 2 -> Entity 1 Role Max. Cardinality
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Entity2ToEntity1RoleMinimumCardinality: """ & obj.Entity2ToEntity1RoleMinimumCardinality & """" ' Entity 2 -> Entity 1 Role Min. Cardinality
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelationshipType: "  & CStr(obj.RelationshipType) ' Relationship Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Entity1ToEntity2RoleMandatory: " & CStr(obj.Entity1ToEntity2RoleMandatory) ' Entity 1 -> Entity 2 Role Mandatory
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Entity2ToEntity1RoleMandatory: " & CStr(obj.Entity2ToEntity1RoleMandatory) ' Entity 2 -> Entity 1 Role Mandatory
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolDisplayed: "   & CStr(obj.SymbolDisplayed ) ' Has Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Entity1ToEntity2RoleDominant: """ & obj.Entity1ToEntity2RoleDominant & """" ' Entity 1 -> Entity 2 Dominance
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Entity2ToEntity1RoleDominant: """ & obj.Entity2ToEntity1RoleDominant & """" ' Entity 2 -> Entity 1 Dominance
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ParentEntity: "      & CStrObj(obj.ParentEntity ) ' Parent Entity
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ChildEntity: "       & CStrObj(obj.ChildEntity  ) ' Child Entity
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Assertion: """       & obj.Assertion       & """" ' Assertion
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Entity1ToEntity2: """ & obj.Entity1ToEntity2 & """" ' Entity 1 to Entity 2
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Entity2ToEntity1: """ & obj.Entity2ToEntity1 & """" ' Entity 2 to Entity 1
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DependentRoleA: "    & CStr(obj.DependentRoleA  ) ' Dependent Role A
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DependentRoleB: "    & CStr(obj.DependentRoleB  ) ' Dependent Role B
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Entity1ToEntity2Role: """ & obj.Entity1ToEntity2Role & """" ' Entity 1 -> Entity 2 Role
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Entity2ToEntity1Role: """ & obj.Entity2ToEntity1Role & """" ' Entity 2 -> Entity 1 Role
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DominantRole: """    & obj.DominantRole    & """" ' Dominant Role
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DependentRole: """   & obj.DependentRole   & """" ' Dependent Role
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Generated: "         & CStr(obj.Generated       ) ' Generate
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Entity1: "           & CStrObj(obj.Entity1      ) ' Entity 1
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Entity2: "           & CStrObj(obj.Entity2      ) ' Entity 2
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Entity1ToEntity2RoleCardinality: """ & obj.Entity1ToEntity2RoleCardinality & """" ' Entity 1 -> Entity 2 Role Cardinality
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Entity2ToEntity1RoleCardinality: """ & obj.Entity2ToEntity1RoleCardinality & """" ' Entity 2 -> Entity 1 Role Cardinality
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Idef1xCardinalityA: """ & obj.Idef1xCardinalityA & """" ' Cardinality IDEF1X A
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Idef1xCardinalityB: """ & obj.Idef1xCardinalityB & """" ' Cardinality IDEF1X B
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCDMRelationship = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCDMInheritanceLink(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCDM Inheritance Link

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object2: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object2      ) ' Second Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object1: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object1      ) ' First Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkDirection: "     & CStr(obj.LinkDirection   ) ' Direction
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExternalDependenciesText: """ & obj.ExternalDependenciesText & """" ' External Dependencies Blob
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ChildEntityName: """ & obj.ChildEntityName & """" ' Child Entity Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ChildEntityCode: """ & obj.ChildEntityCode & """" ' Child Entity Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ParentEntityName: """ & obj.ParentEntityName & """" ' Parent Entity Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ParentEntityCode: """ & obj.ParentEntityCode & """" ' Parent Entity Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Generated: "         & CStr(obj.Generated       ) ' Generate
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolDisplayed: "   & CStr(obj.SymbolDisplayed ) ' Has Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ParentEntity: "      & CStrObj(obj.ParentEntity ) ' Parent Entity
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Inheritance: "       & CStrObj(obj.Inheritance  ) ' Inheritance
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ChildEntity: "       & CStrObj(obj.ChildEntity  ) ' Child Entity
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCDMInheritanceLink = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCDMAssociationLink(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCDM Association Link

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object2: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object2      ) ' Second Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object1: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object1      ) ' First Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkDirection: "     & CStr(obj.LinkDirection   ) ' Direction
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExternalDependenciesText: """ & obj.ExternalDependenciesText & """" ' External Dependencies Blob
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Role: """            & obj.Role            & """" ' Role
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Identifier: "        & CStr(obj.Identifier      ) ' Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MinimumCardinality: """ & obj.MinimumCardinality & """" ' Min. Cardinality of Role
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MaximumCardinality: """ & obj.MaximumCardinality & """" ' Max. Cardinality of Role
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolDisplayed: "   & CStr(obj.SymbolDisplayed ) ' Has Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Entity: "            & CStrObj(obj.Entity       ) ' Entity
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Association: "       & CStrObj(obj.Association  ) ' Association
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Cardinality: """     & obj.Cardinality     & """" ' Cardinality of Role
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolCardinality: """ & obj.SymbolCardinality & """" ' Role Cardinality for symbol
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCDMAssociationLink = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdCDMInheritanceAttribute(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdCDM Inheritance Attribute

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Mandatory: "         & CStr(obj.Mandatory       ) ' Mandatory
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DataStructure: "     & CStrObj(obj.DataStructure) ' Data Structure
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DataItem: "          & CStrObj(obj.DataItem     ) ' Data Item Information
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Unit: """            & obj.Unit            & """" ' Unit
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Format: """          & obj.Format          & """" ' Format
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LowValue: """        & obj.LowValue        & """" ' Minimum Value
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "HighValue: """       & obj.HighValue       & """" ' Maximum Value
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultValue: """    & obj.DefaultValue    & """" ' Default Value
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Uppercase: "         & CStr(obj.Uppercase       ) ' Uppercase
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Lowercase: "         & CStr(obj.Lowercase       ) ' Lowercase
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CannotModify: "      & CStr(obj.CannotModify    ) ' Cannot Modify
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfValues: """    & obj.ListOfValues    & """" ' Values
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClientCheckExpression: """ & obj.ClientCheckExpression & """" ' Client Validation Rule
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ServerCheckExpression: """ & obj.ServerCheckExpression & """" ' Server Validation Rule
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Complete: "          & CStr(obj.Complete        ) ' Complete
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "NoSpace: "           & CStr(obj.NoSpace         ) ' No space
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CharacterCase: "     & CStr(obj.CharacterCase   ) ' Case
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FormatObject: "      & CStrObj(obj.FormatObject ) ' Format object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DataStructureName: """ & obj.DataStructureName & """" ' Using Object Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DataStructureCode: """ & obj.DataStructureCode & """" ' Using Object Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DataStructureType: """ & obj.DataStructureType & """" ' Using Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DataType: """        & obj.DataType        & """" ' Data Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Domain: "            & CStrObj(obj.Domain       ) ' Domain
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Length: "            & CStr(obj.Length          ) ' Length
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Precision: "         & CStr(obj.Precision       ) ' Precision
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DomainOrDataType: """ & obj.DomainOrDataType & """" ' Data Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Inheritance: "       & CStrObj(obj.Inheritance  ) ' Inheritance
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdCDMInheritanceAttribute = Desc

End Function

' Build a the full text description of a PdCDM Association Attribute

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
