         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ManuallyResized: "   & CStr(obj.ManuallyResized ) ' Resized
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepAspect: "        & CStr(obj.KeepAspect      ) ' Keep Aspect Ratio
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepCenter: "        & CStr(obj.KeepCenter      ) ' Keep Center
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepSize: "          & CStr(obj.KeepSize        ) ' Keep Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureType: " & CStr(obj.CustomPictureType) ' Custom Picture Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomTextMode: "    & CStr(obj.CustomTextMode  ) ' Custom Picture Text Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureID: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureID & """" ' Background Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureID: """ & obj.CustomPictureID & """" ' Custom Picture ID

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureFile: """ & obj.CustomPictureFile & """" ' Custom Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomShapeType: "   & CStr(obj.CustomShapeType ) ' Custom Shape Type

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubSymbolsLayout: """ & obj.SubSymbolsLayout & """" ' Sub-Symbols Layout
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdEAMFormSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdEAMOrganizationChartDiagram(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdEAM Organization Chart

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayPreferences: """ & obj.DisplayPreferences & """" ' Display Preferences
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Scale: "             & CStr(obj.Scale           ) ' Scale
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PaperSize: "         & obj.PaperSize.AsText        ' Paper Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PaperSource: "       & CStr(obj.PaperSource     ) ' Paper Source
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageMargins: "       & obj.PageMargins.AsText      ' Page Margins
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageFormat: "        & CStr(obj.PageFormat      ) ' Page Format
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageOrientation: "   & CStr(obj.PageOrientation ) ' Page Orientation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Diagram Flags
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageFooterTemplate: """ & obj.PageFooterTemplate & """" ' Page Footer Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageHeaderTemplate: """ & obj.PageHeaderTemplate & """" ' Page Header Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageNumberTemplate: """ & obj.PageNumberTemplate & """" ' Page Number Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SwimlaneHeaderHeight: " & CStr(obj.SwimlaneHeaderHeight) ' Swimlane Header Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SetAsDefault: "      & CStr(obj.SetAsDefault    ) ' Is Default
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdEAMOrganizationChartDiagram = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdEAMOrganizationUnit(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdEAM Organization Unit

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UseParentNamespace: " & CStr(obj.UseParentNamespace) ' Use Parent Namespace

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolDisplayed: "   & CStr(obj.SymbolDisplayed ) ' Has Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultDiagram: "    & CStrObj(obj.DefaultDiagram) ' Default Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Composite: "         & CStr(obj.Composite       ) ' Composite
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Level: "             & CStr(obj.Level           ) ' Level
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PreviewDiagram: "    & CStrObj(obj.PreviewDiagram) ' Preview Diagram

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Email: """           & obj.Email           & """" ' Email
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdEAMOrganizationUnit = Desc

End Function

   End If

Function DescribePdEAMTechnologyInfrastructureDiagram(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdEAM Technology Infrastructure Diagram

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayPreferences: """ & obj.DisplayPreferences & """" ' Display Preferences
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Scale: "             & CStr(obj.Scale           ) ' Scale
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PaperSize: "         & obj.PaperSize.AsText        ' Paper Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PaperSource: "       & CStr(obj.PaperSource     ) ' Paper Source
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageMargins: "       & obj.PageMargins.AsText      ' Page Margins
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageFormat: "        & CStr(obj.PageFormat      ) ' Page Format
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageOrientation: "   & CStr(obj.PageOrientation ) ' Page Orientation

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageFooterTemplate: """ & obj.PageFooterTemplate & """" ' Page Footer Template

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SwimlaneHeaderHeight: " & CStr(obj.SwimlaneHeaderHeight) ' Swimlane Header Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SetAsDefault: "      & CStr(obj.SetAsDefault    ) ' Is Default

   Else

   End If

   DescribePdEAMTechnologyInfrastructureDiagram = Desc

Function DescribePdEAMRoleSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdEAM Role Symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name

' Build a the full text description of a PdEAM Role

      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview

   End If

' Build a the full text description of a PdEAM Software Server Symbol

   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location

   Else

   End If

   DescribePdEAMSoftwareServerSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdEAMSoftwareServer(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdEAM Software Server

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UseParentNamespace: " & CStr(obj.UseParentNamespace) ' Use Parent Namespace
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PackageOptionsText: """ & obj.PackageOptionsText & """" ' Package Options
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolDisplayed: "   & CStr(obj.SymbolDisplayed ) ' Has Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultDiagram: "    & CStrObj(obj.DefaultDiagram) ' Default Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Composite: "         & CStr(obj.Composite       ) ' Composite
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Level: "             & CStr(obj.Level           ) ' Level
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PreviewDiagram: "    & CStrObj(obj.PreviewDiagram) ' Preview Diagram

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Manufacturer: """    & obj.Manufacturer    & """" ' Manufacturer
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SerialNumber: """    & obj.SerialNumber    & """" ' Serial Number
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Version: """         & obj.Version         & """" ' Version

   End If

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ReusedProcess: "     & CStrObj(obj.ReusedProcess) ' Reused Process
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdEAMProcess = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdEAMProcessSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdEAM Process Symbol

      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color

Function DescribePdEAMDocument(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdEAM Document

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation

      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdEAMDocument = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdEAMReportDocument(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdEAM Report Document

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator

   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent

Function DescribePdEAMOperation(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdEAM Operation

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder

Function DescribePdEAMRoleAssociation(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdEAM Role Association

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object1: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object1      ) ' First Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkedObject: "      & CStrObj(obj.LinkedObject ) ' Linked Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RolePlayer: "        & CStrObj(obj.RolePlayer   ) ' Role Player
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AssociationType: """ & obj.AssociationType & """" ' Type
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdEAMRoleAssociation = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DispID: "            & CStr(obj.DispID          ) ' DISPID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PublicName: """      & obj.PublicName      & """" ' Public Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Event: """           & obj.Event           & """" ' Action
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SkipLink: "          & CStr(obj.SkipLink        ) ' Skip Link
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Recursive: "         & CStr(obj.Recursive       ) ' Recursive
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IsImpact: "          & CStr(obj.IsImpact        ) ' Is Impact

   Else

   End If

Function DescribePdIAMImpactAnalysisObject(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdIAM Analysis Object

   Dim Desc

      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AnalysisObjectType: """ & obj.AnalysisObjectType & """" ' Source Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AnalysisType: """    & obj.AnalysisType    & """" ' Impact Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ImpactedModel: "     & CStrObj(obj.ImpactedModel) ' Impacted Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Event: """           & obj.Event           & """" ' Action
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FullPath: """        & obj.FullPath        & """" ' Propagation Path
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceObject: "      & CStrObj(obj.SourceObject ) ' Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PrimaryObject: "     & CStrObj(obj.PrimaryObject) ' Primary Impacted Object

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceObjectID: """  & obj.SourceObjectID  & """" ' Source Object ID

   End If

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PictureFillMode: "   & CStr(obj.PictureFillMode ) ' Picture Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AutoAdjustToText: "  & CStr(obj.AutoAdjustToText) ' Auto Adjust to Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ManuallyResized: "   & CStr(obj.ManuallyResized ) ' Resized
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepAspect: "        & CStr(obj.KeepAspect      ) ' Keep Aspect Ratio
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepCenter: "        & CStr(obj.KeepCenter      ) ' Keep Center
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepSize: "          & CStr(obj.KeepSize        ) ' Keep Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureType: " & CStr(obj.CustomPictureType) ' Custom Picture Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomTextMode: "    & CStr(obj.CustomTextMode  ) ' Custom Picture Text Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureID: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureID & """" ' Background Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureID: """ & obj.CustomPictureID & """" ' Custom Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureFile: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureFile & """" ' Background Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureFile: """ & obj.CustomPictureFile & """" ' Custom Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomShapeType: "   & CStr(obj.CustomShapeType ) ' Custom Shape Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FontList: """        & obj.FontList        & """" ' Font List
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object: "            & CStrObj(obj.Object       ) ' Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubObjects: """      & obj.SubObjects      & """" ' Sub-objects Blob
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconMode: "          & CStr(obj.IconMode        ) ' Icon Mode

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubSymbolsLayout: """ & obj.SubSymbolsLayout & """" ' Sub-Symbols Layout

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "EmptyCompartments: " & CStr(obj.EmptyCompartments) ' Symbol Empty Compartments
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdIAMImpactAnalysisObjectSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdIAMImpactLinkSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdIAM Analysis Link

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfPoints: "      & obj.ListOfPoints.AsText     ' List Points
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CornerStyle: "       & CStr(obj.CornerStyle     ) ' Corner Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ArrowStyle: "        & CStr(obj.ArrowStyle      ) ' Arrows
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkPosition: "      & obj.LinkPosition.AsText     ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkSize: "          & obj.LinkSize.AsText         ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceSymbol: "      & CStrObj(obj.SourceSymbol ) ' Source Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationSymbol: " & CStrObj(obj.DestinationSymbol) ' Destination Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CenterTextOffset: "  & obj.CenterTextOffset.AsText ' Centered Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceTextOffset: "  & obj.SourceTextOffset.AsText ' Source Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationTextOffset: " & obj.DestinationTextOffset.AsText ' Destination Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TextStyle: "         & CStr(obj.TextStyle       ) ' Text Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FontColor: "         & CStr(obj.FontColor       ) ' Font Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FontName: """        & obj.FontName        & """" ' Font Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CenterText: """      & obj.CenterText      & """" ' Center Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceText: """      & obj.SourceText      & """" ' Source Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationText: """ & obj.DestinationText & """" ' Destination Text
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdIAMImpactLinkSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdMTMModel(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdMTM Merise Process Model

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UseParentNamespace: " & CStr(obj.UseParentNamespace) ' Use Parent Namespace
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PackageOptionsText: """ & obj.PackageOptionsText & """" ' Package Options
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolDisplayed: "   & CStr(obj.SymbolDisplayed ) ' Has Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultDiagram: "    & CStrObj(obj.DefaultDiagram) ' Default Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModelOptionsText: """ & obj.ModelOptionsText & """" ' Model Options
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RepositoryInformation: """ & obj.RepositoryInformation & """" ' Repository Information
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UpToDateStatus: "    & CStr(obj.UpToDateStatus  ) ' Up To Date Status
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RepositoryID: """    & obj.RepositoryID    & """" ' Repository Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtractionVersionID: " & CStr(obj.ExtractionVersionID) ' Model Extraction Version Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtractionVersion: """ & obj.ExtractionVersion & """" ' Model Extraction Version
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtractionBranchID: " & CStr(obj.ExtractionBranchID) ' Model Extraction Branch Identifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtractionDate: "    & CStr(obj.ExtractionDate  ) ' Model Extraction Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtractionEndDate: " & CStr(obj.ExtractionEndDate) ' Model Extraction End Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Author: """          & obj.Author          & """" ' Author
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Version: """         & obj.Version         & """" ' Version
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ApplicationVersion: """ & obj.ApplicationVersion & """" ' Application Version
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Filename: """        & obj.Filename        & """" ' Filename
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modified: "          & CStr(obj.Modified        ) ' Modified
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExternalDependenciesText: """ & obj.ExternalDependenciesText & """" ' External Dependencies Blob
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceModelDocument: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceModelDocument) ' 
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdMTMModel = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayPreferences: """ & obj.DisplayPreferences & """" ' Display Preferences
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Scale: "             & CStr(obj.Scale           ) ' Scale
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PaperSize: "         & obj.PaperSize.AsText        ' Paper Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PaperSource: "       & CStr(obj.PaperSource     ) ' Paper Source
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageMargins: "       & obj.PageMargins.AsText      ' Page Margins
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageFormat: "        & CStr(obj.PageFormat      ) ' Page Format
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageOrientation: "   & CStr(obj.PageOrientation ) ' Page Orientation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Diagram Flags
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageFooterTemplate: """ & obj.PageFooterTemplate & """" ' Page Footer Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageHeaderTemplate: """ & obj.PageHeaderTemplate & """" ' Page Header Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageNumberTemplate: """ & obj.PageNumberTemplate & """" ' Page Number Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SwimlaneHeaderHeight: " & CStr(obj.SwimlaneHeaderHeight) ' Swimlane Header Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SetAsDefault: "      & CStr(obj.SetAsDefault    ) ' Is Default
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdMTMFlowDiagram = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdMTMConceptualDiagram(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdMTM Conceptual Diagram

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayPreferences: """ & obj.DisplayPreferences & """" ' Display Preferences
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Scale: "             & CStr(obj.Scale           ) ' Scale
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PaperSize: "         & obj.PaperSize.AsText        ' Paper Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PaperSource: "       & CStr(obj.PaperSource     ) ' Paper Source
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageMargins: "       & obj.PageMargins.AsText      ' Page Margins
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageFormat: "        & CStr(obj.PageFormat      ) ' Page Format
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageOrientation: "   & CStr(obj.PageOrientation ) ' Page Orientation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Diagram Flags
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageFooterTemplate: """ & obj.PageFooterTemplate & """" ' Page Footer Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageHeaderTemplate: """ & obj.PageHeaderTemplate & """" ' Page Header Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageNumberTemplate: """ & obj.PageNumberTemplate & """" ' Page Number Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SwimlaneHeaderHeight: " & CStr(obj.SwimlaneHeaderHeight) ' Swimlane Header Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SetAsDefault: "      & CStr(obj.SetAsDefault    ) ' Is Default
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdMTMConceptualDiagram = Desc

End Function

      End If
   Else

   End If

' Build a the full text description of a PdMTM Operation

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then

         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else

   End If

Function DescribePdMTMPhase(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdMTM Phase

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Synchronization: """ & obj.Synchronization & """" ' Synchronization
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolDisplayed: "   & CStr(obj.SymbolDisplayed ) ' Has Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Actor: "             & CStrObj(obj.Actor        ) ' Actor
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Period: """          & obj.Period          & """" ' Period
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Duration: """        & obj.Duration        & """" ' Duration

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Type: "              & CStr(obj.Type            ) ' Type
      End If
   Else

   End If

   DescribePdMTMPhase = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Data: "              & CStrObj(obj.Data         ) ' Data
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object: "            & CStrObj(obj.Object       ) ' Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CRUD: "              & CStr(obj.CRUD            ) ' CRUD
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreateAccess: "      & CStr(obj.CreateAccess    ) ' Create
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ReadAccess: "        & CStr(obj.ReadAccess      ) ' Read
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DeleteAccess: "      & CStr(obj.DeleteAccess    ) ' Delete
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UpdateAccess: "      & CStr(obj.UpdateAccess    ) ' Update
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdMTMDataAccess = Desc

Function DescribePdMTMPackageSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdMTM Package Symbol

      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then

         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BrushStyle: "        & CStr(obj.BrushStyle      ) ' Brush Style

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepCenter: "        & CStr(obj.KeepCenter      ) ' Keep Center

' Build a the full text description of a PdMTM Emission Rule Symbol

   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BrushStyle: "        & CStr(obj.BrushStyle      ) ' Brush Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientFillMode: "  & CStr(obj.GradientFillMode) ' Gradient Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientEndColor: "  & CStr(obj.GradientEndColor) ' Gradient End Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PictureFillMode: "   & CStr(obj.PictureFillMode ) ' Picture Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AutoAdjustToText: "  & CStr(obj.AutoAdjustToText) ' Auto Adjust to Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ManuallyResized: "   & CStr(obj.ManuallyResized ) ' Resized
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepAspect: "        & CStr(obj.KeepAspect      ) ' Keep Aspect Ratio
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepCenter: "        & CStr(obj.KeepCenter      ) ' Keep Center
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepSize: "          & CStr(obj.KeepSize        ) ' Keep Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureType: " & CStr(obj.CustomPictureType) ' Custom Picture Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomTextMode: "    & CStr(obj.CustomTextMode  ) ' Custom Picture Text Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureID: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureID & """" ' Background Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureID: """ & obj.CustomPictureID & """" ' Custom Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureFile: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureFile & """" ' Background Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureFile: """ & obj.CustomPictureFile & """" ' Custom Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomShapeType: "   & CStr(obj.CustomShapeType ) ' Custom Shape Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FontList: """        & obj.FontList        & """" ' Font List
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object: "            & CStrObj(obj.Object       ) ' Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubObjects: """      & obj.SubObjects      & """" ' Sub-objects Blob
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdMTMEmissionRuleSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdMTMOperationSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdMTM Operation Symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BrushStyle: "        & CStr(obj.BrushStyle      ) ' Brush Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientFillMode: "  & CStr(obj.GradientFillMode) ' Gradient Fill Mode

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PictureFillMode: "   & CStr(obj.PictureFillMode ) ' Picture Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AutoAdjustToText: "  & CStr(obj.AutoAdjustToText) ' Auto Adjust to Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ManuallyResized: "   & CStr(obj.ManuallyResized ) ' Resized
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepAspect: "        & CStr(obj.KeepAspect      ) ' Keep Aspect Ratio
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepCenter: "        & CStr(obj.KeepCenter      ) ' Keep Center

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceSymbol: "      & CStrObj(obj.SourceSymbol ) ' Source Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationSymbol: " & CStrObj(obj.DestinationSymbol) ' Destination Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CenterTextOffset: "  & obj.CenterTextOffset.AsText ' Centered Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceTextOffset: "  & obj.SourceTextOffset.AsText ' Source Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationTextOffset: " & obj.DestinationTextOffset.AsText ' Destination Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FontList: """        & obj.FontList        & """" ' Font List
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object: "            & CStrObj(obj.Object       ) ' Object
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdMTMPhaseEmissionSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdMTMOperationTriggeringSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdMTM Operation Triggering Symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfPoints: "      & obj.ListOfPoints.AsText     ' List Points
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CornerStyle: "       & CStr(obj.CornerStyle     ) ' Corner Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ArrowStyle: "        & CStr(obj.ArrowStyle      ) ' Arrows
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkPosition: "      & obj.LinkPosition.AsText     ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkSize: "          & obj.LinkSize.AsText         ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceSymbol: "      & CStrObj(obj.SourceSymbol ) ' Source Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationSymbol: " & CStrObj(obj.DestinationSymbol) ' Destination Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CenterTextOffset: "  & obj.CenterTextOffset.AsText ' Centered Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceTextOffset: "  & obj.SourceTextOffset.AsText ' Source Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationTextOffset: " & obj.DestinationTextOffset.AsText ' Destination Text Offset

      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdMTMOperationTriggeringSymbol = Desc

End Function

Function DescribePdOOMModel(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Object-Oriented Model

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
