Function DescribePdOOMPackage(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Package

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UseParentNamespace: " & CStr(obj.UseParentNamespace) ' Use Parent Namespace
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PackageOptionsText: """ & obj.PackageOptionsText & """" ' Package Options
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolDisplayed: "   & CStr(obj.SymbolDisplayed ) ' Has Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultDiagram: "    & CStrObj(obj.DefaultDiagram) ' Default Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FullyQualifiedName: """ & obj.FullyQualifiedName & """" ' Fully Qualified Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AllAnnotations: """  & obj.AllAnnotations  & """" ' All Annotations
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMPackage = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "NameGeneric: """     & obj.NameGeneric     & """" ' Generic Name

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "QualifiedCode: """   & obj.QualifiedCode   & """" ' Qualified Code

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AllAnnotations: """  & obj.AllAnnotations  & """" ' All Annotations
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMInterface = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdOOMActor(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Actor

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolDisplayed: "   & CStr(obj.SymbolDisplayed ) ' Has Symbol
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMActor = Desc

End Function

      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Type: """            & obj.Type            & """" ' Component Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "WebService: "        & CStr(obj.WebService      ) ' WebService

      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMComponentInstance = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdOOMAnnotation(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Annotation

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Owner: "             & CStrObj(obj.Owner        ) ' Owner
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Annotation Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AnnotationType: "    & CStrObj(obj.AnnotationType) ' Annotation Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Text: """            & obj.Text            & """" ' Annotation Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Syntax: """          & obj.Syntax          & """" ' Annotation Syntax
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Name with Classifier
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMAnnotation = Desc

End Function

Function DescribePdOOMAttributeValue(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Attribute Value

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location

         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Name with Classifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Value: """           & obj.Value           & """" ' Value
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ParentObject: "      & CStrObj(obj.ParentObject ) ' Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Attribute: "         & CStrObj(obj.Attribute    ) ' Attribute
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayValue: """    & obj.DisplayValue    & """" ' Display Value
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Class: "             & CStrObj(obj.Class        ) ' Class
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MigratedAssociation: " & CStrObj(obj.MigratedAssociation) ' Migrated Association

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DataType: """        & obj.DataType        & """" ' Data Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Multiplicity: """    & obj.Multiplicity    & """" ' Multiplicity
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "InitialValue: """    & obj.InitialValue    & """" ' Initial Value
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Static: "            & CStr(obj.Static          ) ' Static
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Derived: "           & CStr(obj.Derived         ) ' Derived
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Persistent: "        & CStr(obj.Persistent      ) ' Persistence
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Displayed: "         & CStr(obj.Displayed       ) ' Displayed
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PersistentDataType: """ & obj.PersistentDataType & """" ' Persistent Data Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PersistentLength: "  & CStr(obj.PersistentLength) ' Persistent Length
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PersistentPrecision: " & CStr(obj.PersistentPrecision) ' Persistent Precision
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PersistentClassGeneration: """ & obj.PersistentClassGeneration & """" ' Persistent Class Generation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PersistentCode: """  & obj.PersistentCode  & """" ' Persistent Code

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Format: """          & obj.Format          & """" ' Format

   End If

' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Operation

   Dim Desc

      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayVisibilityMarker: """ & obj.DisplayVisibilityMarker & """" ' Display Visibility Marker

   Else

   End If

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenericObject: "     & CStrObj(obj.GenericObject) ' Generic Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DerivationConstraint: """ & obj.DerivationConstraint & """" ' Derivation Constraint
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMTypeParameter = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdOOMTypeParameterValue(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Type Parameter Value

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TypeParameter: "     & CStrObj(obj.TypeParameter) ' Type Parameter

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Name with Classifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMTypeParameterValue = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdOOMInnerLink(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Inner Link

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "InnerClassifier: "   & CStrObj(obj.InnerClassifier) ' Inner Classifier

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMInnerLink = Desc

End Function

   DescribePdOOMInstanceLink = Desc

Function DescribePdOOMUseCaseAssociation(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Use Case Association

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object2: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object2      ) ' Second Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object1: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object1      ) ' First Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultMapping: "    & CStrObj(obj.DefaultMapping) ' Mapping
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayedStereotype: """ & obj.DisplayedStereotype & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolDisplayed: "   & CStr(obj.SymbolDisplayed ) ' Has Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayedRules: """  & obj.DisplayedRules  & """" ' Constraint
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Source: "            & CStrObj(obj.Source       ) ' Source
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Destination: "       & CStrObj(obj.Destination  ) ' Destination
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Primary: "           & CStr(obj.Primary         ) ' Orientation
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMUseCaseAssociation = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ChildObject: "       & CStrObj(obj.ChildObject  ) ' Child Object
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMRequireLink = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdOOMAssemblyConnector(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Assembly Connector

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object2: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object2      ) ' Second Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object1: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object1      ) ' First Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DefaultMapping: "    & CStrObj(obj.DefaultMapping) ' Mapping
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayedStereotype: """ & obj.DisplayedStereotype & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolDisplayed: "   & CStr(obj.SymbolDisplayed ) ' Has Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayedRules: """  & obj.DisplayedRules  & """" ' Constraint
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClientObject: "      & CStrObj(obj.ClientObject ) ' Client Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SupplierObject: "    & CStrObj(obj.SupplierObject) ' Supplier Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Interface: "         & CStrObj(obj.Interface    ) ' Interface
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMAssemblyConnector = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator

      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMInteractionReference = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Name with Classifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DiagramType: "       & CStr(obj.DiagramType     ) ' Extended Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Condition: """       & obj.Condition       & """" ' Condition
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & CStr(obj.Size            ) ' Fragment Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FragmentType: """    & obj.FragmentType    & """" ' Fragment Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Multiple: "          & CStr(obj.Multiple        ) ' Multiple
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FragmentName: """    & obj.FragmentName    & """" ' Fragment Name
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMInteractionFragment = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdOOMInteractionActivity(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Interaction Activity

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Arguments: """       & obj.Arguments       & """" ' Arguments
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ReturnValue: """     & obj.ReturnValue     & """" ' Return Value
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Keyword: """         & obj.Keyword         & """" ' Keyword
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Name with Classifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DiagramType: "       & CStr(obj.DiagramType     ) ' Extended Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ReferencedDiagram: " & CStrObj(obj.ReferencedDiagram) ' Referenced Diagram
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMInteractionActivity = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SequenceNumber: """  & obj.SequenceNumber  & """" ' Sequence Number

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OwnerLink: "         & CStrObj(obj.OwnerLink    ) ' Owner Link
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMMessage = Desc

End Function

      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier

      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMUMLPackageDiagram = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdOOMUseCaseDiagram(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Use Case Diagram

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayPreferences: """ & obj.DisplayPreferences & """" ' Display Preferences
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Scale: "             & CStr(obj.Scale           ) ' Scale
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PaperSize: "         & obj.PaperSize.AsText        ' Paper Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PaperSource: "       & CStr(obj.PaperSource     ) ' Paper Source
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageMargins: "       & obj.PageMargins.AsText      ' Page Margins
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageFormat: "        & CStr(obj.PageFormat      ) ' Page Format
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageOrientation: "   & CStr(obj.PageOrientation ) ' Page Orientation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Diagram Flags
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageFooterTemplate: """ & obj.PageFooterTemplate & """" ' Page Footer Template

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SwimlaneHeaderHeight: " & CStr(obj.SwimlaneHeaderHeight) ' Swimlane Header Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin

      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMUseCaseDiagram = Desc

End Function

Function DescribePdOOMDeploymentDiagram(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Deployment Diagram

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayPreferences: """ & obj.DisplayPreferences & """" ' Display Preferences
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Scale: "             & CStr(obj.Scale           ) ' Scale
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PaperSize: "         & obj.PaperSize.AsText        ' Paper Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PaperSource: "       & CStr(obj.PaperSource     ) ' Paper Source
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageMargins: "       & obj.PageMargins.AsText      ' Page Margins
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageFormat: "        & CStr(obj.PageFormat      ) ' Page Format
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageOrientation: "   & CStr(obj.PageOrientation ) ' Page Orientation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Diagram Flags
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageFooterTemplate: """ & obj.PageFooterTemplate & """" ' Page Footer Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageHeaderTemplate: """ & obj.PageHeaderTemplate & """" ' Page Header Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageNumberTemplate: """ & obj.PageNumberTemplate & """" ' Page Number Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SwimlaneHeaderHeight: " & CStr(obj.SwimlaneHeaderHeight) ' Swimlane Header Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SetAsDefault: "      & CStr(obj.SetAsDefault    ) ' Is Default
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMDeploymentDiagram = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdOOMCommunicationDiagram(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Communication Diagram

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayPreferences: """ & obj.DisplayPreferences & """" ' Display Preferences
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Scale: "             & CStr(obj.Scale           ) ' Scale
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PaperSize: "         & obj.PaperSize.AsText        ' Paper Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PaperSource: "       & CStr(obj.PaperSource     ) ' Paper Source
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageMargins: "       & obj.PageMargins.AsText      ' Page Margins
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageFormat: "        & CStr(obj.PageFormat      ) ' Page Format
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageOrientation: "   & CStr(obj.PageOrientation ) ' Page Orientation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Diagram Flags
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageFooterTemplate: """ & obj.PageFooterTemplate & """" ' Page Footer Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageHeaderTemplate: """ & obj.PageHeaderTemplate & """" ' Page Header Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageNumberTemplate: """ & obj.PageNumberTemplate & """" ' Page Number Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SwimlaneHeaderHeight: " & CStr(obj.SwimlaneHeaderHeight) ' Swimlane Header Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SetAsDefault: "      & CStr(obj.SetAsDefault    ) ' Is Default
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMCommunicationDiagram = Desc

End Function

   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then

      Else

Function DescribePdOOMIdentifier(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Identifier

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Classifier: "        & CStrObj(obj.Classifier   ) ' Classifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Attribute: "         & CStrObj(obj.Attribute    ) ' Attribute
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Primary: "           & CStr(obj.Primary         ) ' Primary Identifier
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMIdentifier = Desc

End Function

Function DescribePdOOMVariable(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Variable

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation

   End If

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Name with Classifier

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OperationArguments: """ & obj.OperationArguments & """" ' Operation Arguments
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "EventArguments: """  & obj.EventArguments  & """" ' Event Arguments

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LabelWithArguments: """ & obj.LabelWithArguments & """" ' Event, Name and arguments
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMTransition = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Level: "             & CStr(obj.Level           ) ' Level
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PreviewDiagram: "    & CStrObj(obj.PreviewDiagram) ' Preview Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Classifier: "        & CStrObj(obj.Classifier   ) ' Classifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SmallDisplayName: """ & obj.SmallDisplayName & """" ' Name
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMState = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdOOMAction(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Action

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ConditionAlias: """  & obj.ConditionAlias  & """" ' Condition Alias
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ConditionExpression: """ & obj.ConditionExpression & """" ' Condition Expression
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "EventArguments: """  & obj.EventArguments  & """" ' Event Arguments
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PredefinedEvent: """ & obj.PredefinedEvent & """" ' Predefined Event
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayedCondition: """ & obj.DisplayedCondition & """" ' Condition
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TriggerEventText: """ & obj.TriggerEventText & """" ' Trigger Event
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "TriggerEventObject: " & CStrObj(obj.TriggerEventObject) ' Trigger Event Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Operation: "         & CStrObj(obj.Operation    ) ' Operation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OperationArguments: """ & obj.OperationArguments & """" ' Operation Arguments
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Label: """           & obj.Label           & """" ' Event and Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LabelWithArguments: """ & obj.LabelWithArguments & """" ' Event, Name and arguments
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMAction = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdOOMEvent(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Event

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transformation: "    & CStrObj(obj.Transformation) ' Transformation

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ActivityTermination: " & CStr(obj.ActivityTermination) ' End Activity Termination
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMEnd = Desc

End Function

   End If

Function DescribePdOOMClassSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Class symbol

   Dim Desc

      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then

      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color

' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Actor Symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color

      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMActorSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdOOMUseCaseSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Use Case Symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfPoints: "      & obj.ListOfPoints.AsText     ' List Points
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CornerStyle: "       & CStr(obj.CornerStyle     ) ' Corner Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ArrowStyle: "        & CStr(obj.ArrowStyle      ) ' Arrows
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkPosition: "      & obj.LinkPosition.AsText     ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkSize: "          & obj.LinkSize.AsText         ' Size

      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMInstanceLinkSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdOOMCollaborationInstanceLinkSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Instance Link symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color

' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Component Interface Symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
