         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BrushStyle: "        & CStr(obj.BrushStyle      ) ' Brush Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientFillMode: "  & CStr(obj.GradientFillMode) ' Gradient Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientEndColor: "  & CStr(obj.GradientEndColor) ' Gradient End Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PictureFillMode: "   & CStr(obj.PictureFillMode ) ' Picture Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AutoAdjustToText: "  & CStr(obj.AutoAdjustToText) ' Auto Adjust to Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ManuallyResized: "   & CStr(obj.ManuallyResized ) ' Resized
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepAspect: "        & CStr(obj.KeepAspect      ) ' Keep Aspect Ratio
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepCenter: "        & CStr(obj.KeepCenter      ) ' Keep Center
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepSize: "          & CStr(obj.KeepSize        ) ' Keep Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureType: " & CStr(obj.CustomPictureType) ' Custom Picture Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomTextMode: "    & CStr(obj.CustomTextMode  ) ' Custom Picture Text Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureID: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureID & """" ' Background Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureID: """ & obj.CustomPictureID & """" ' Custom Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureFile: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureFile & """" ' Background Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureFile: """ & obj.CustomPictureFile & """" ' Custom Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomShapeType: "   & CStr(obj.CustomShapeType ) ' Custom Shape Type
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMComponentInterfaceSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdOOMObjectNodeSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Object Node symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BrushStyle: "        & CStr(obj.BrushStyle      ) ' Brush Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientFillMode: "  & CStr(obj.GradientFillMode) ' Gradient Fill Mode

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ManuallyResized: "   & CStr(obj.ManuallyResized ) ' Resized
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepAspect: "        & CStr(obj.KeepAspect      ) ' Keep Aspect Ratio
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepCenter: "        & CStr(obj.KeepCenter      ) ' Keep Center

   Else

   End If

' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Message Symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfPoints: "      & obj.ListOfPoints.AsText     ' List Points

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationSymbol: " & CStrObj(obj.DestinationSymbol) ' Destination Symbol

      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMMessageSymbol = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureFile: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureFile & """" ' Background Picture File

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomShapeType: "   & CStr(obj.CustomShapeType ) ' Custom Shape Type

   Else

   End If

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BrushStyle: "        & CStr(obj.BrushStyle      ) ' Brush Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientFillMode: "  & CStr(obj.GradientFillMode) ' Gradient Fill Mode

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PictureFillMode: "   & CStr(obj.PictureFillMode ) ' Picture Fill Mode

      End If
   Else

   End If

   DescribePdOOMNodeSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdOOMCmpiSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Component Instance Symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BrushStyle: "        & CStr(obj.BrushStyle      ) ' Brush Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientFillMode: "  & CStr(obj.GradientFillMode) ' Gradient Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientEndColor: "  & CStr(obj.GradientEndColor) ' Gradient End Color

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AutoAdjustToText: "  & CStr(obj.AutoAdjustToText) ' Auto Adjust to Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ManuallyResized: "   & CStr(obj.ManuallyResized ) ' Resized
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepAspect: "        & CStr(obj.KeepAspect      ) ' Keep Aspect Ratio
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepCenter: "        & CStr(obj.KeepCenter      ) ' Keep Center

   DescribePdOOMLifelineSymbol = Desc

Function DescribePdOOMInnerLinkSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Inner Link Symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfPoints: "      & obj.ListOfPoints.AsText     ' List Points
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CornerStyle: "       & CStr(obj.CornerStyle     ) ' Corner Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ArrowStyle: "        & CStr(obj.ArrowStyle      ) ' Arrows
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkPosition: "      & obj.LinkPosition.AsText     ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkSize: "          & obj.LinkSize.AsText         ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceSymbol: "      & CStrObj(obj.SourceSymbol ) ' Source Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationSymbol: " & CStrObj(obj.DestinationSymbol) ' Destination Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CenterTextOffset: "  & obj.CenterTextOffset.AsText ' Centered Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceTextOffset: "  & obj.SourceTextOffset.AsText ' Source Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationTextOffset: " & obj.DestinationTextOffset.AsText ' Destination Text Offset

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubSymbolsLayout: """ & obj.SubSymbolsLayout & """" ' Sub-Symbols Layout
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMInnerLinkSymbol = Desc

End Function

   End If

Function DescribePdOOMGeneralizationSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdOOM Generalization symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfPoints: "      & obj.ListOfPoints.AsText     ' List Points
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CornerStyle: "       & CStr(obj.CornerStyle     ) ' Corner Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ArrowStyle: "        & CStr(obj.ArrowStyle      ) ' Arrows
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkPosition: "      & obj.LinkPosition.AsText     ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkSize: "          & obj.LinkSize.AsText         ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceSymbol: "      & CStrObj(obj.SourceSymbol ) ' Source Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationSymbol: " & CStrObj(obj.DestinationSymbol) ' Destination Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CenterTextOffset: "  & obj.CenterTextOffset.AsText ' Centered Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceTextOffset: "  & obj.SourceTextOffset.AsText ' Source Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationTextOffset: " & obj.DestinationTextOffset.AsText ' Destination Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FontList: """        & obj.FontList        & """" ' Font List
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object: "            & CStrObj(obj.Object       ) ' Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolContent: """   & obj.SymbolContent   & """" ' Symbol Content
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubSymbolsLayout: """ & obj.SubSymbolsLayout & """" ' Sub-Symbols Layout
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMGeneralizationSymbol = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfPoints: "      & obj.ListOfPoints.AsText     ' List Points
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CornerStyle: "       & CStr(obj.CornerStyle     ) ' Corner Style

      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdOOMFlowSymbol = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureID: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureID & """" ' Background Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureID: """ & obj.CustomPictureID & """" ' Custom Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureFile: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureFile & """" ' Background Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureFile: """ & obj.CustomPictureFile & """" ' Custom Picture File

      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   End If

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMPhysicalDiagram = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdPDMMultidimensionalDiagram(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Multidimensional Diagram

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""

      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent

Function DescribePdPDMPackageSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Package Symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BrushStyle: "        & CStr(obj.BrushStyle      ) ' Brush Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientFillMode: "  & CStr(obj.GradientFillMode) ' Gradient Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientEndColor: "  & CStr(obj.GradientEndColor) ' Gradient End Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PictureFillMode: "   & CStr(obj.PictureFillMode ) ' Picture Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AutoAdjustToText: "  & CStr(obj.AutoAdjustToText) ' Auto Adjust to Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ManuallyResized: "   & CStr(obj.ManuallyResized ) ' Resized
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepAspect: "        & CStr(obj.KeepAspect      ) ' Keep Aspect Ratio
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepCenter: "        & CStr(obj.KeepCenter      ) ' Keep Center
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepSize: "          & CStr(obj.KeepSize        ) ' Keep Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureType: " & CStr(obj.CustomPictureType) ' Custom Picture Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomTextMode: "    & CStr(obj.CustomTextMode  ) ' Custom Picture Text Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureID: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureID & """" ' Background Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureID: """ & obj.CustomPictureID & """" ' Custom Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureFile: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureFile & """" ' Background Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureFile: """ & obj.CustomPictureFile & """" ' Custom Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomShapeType: "   & CStr(obj.CustomShapeType ) ' Custom Shape Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FontList: """        & obj.FontList        & """" ' Font List
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object: "            & CStrObj(obj.Object       ) ' Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubObjects: """      & obj.SubObjects      & """" ' Sub-objects Blob
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconMode: "          & CStr(obj.IconMode        ) ' Icon Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolContent: """   & obj.SymbolContent   & """" ' Symbol Content
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubSymbolsLayout: """ & obj.SubSymbolsLayout & """" ' Sub-Symbols Layout
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CompositeView: "     & CStr(obj.CompositeView   ) ' Composite View
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMPackageSymbol = Desc

End Function

      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BrushStyle: "        & CStr(obj.BrushStyle      ) ' Brush Style

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PictureFillMode: "   & CStr(obj.PictureFillMode ) ' Picture Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AutoAdjustToText: "  & CStr(obj.AutoAdjustToText) ' Auto Adjust to Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ManuallyResized: "   & CStr(obj.ManuallyResized ) ' Resized
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepAspect: "        & CStr(obj.KeepAspect      ) ' Keep Aspect Ratio
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepCenter: "        & CStr(obj.KeepCenter      ) ' Keep Center
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepSize: "          & CStr(obj.KeepSize        ) ' Keep Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureType: " & CStr(obj.CustomPictureType) ' Custom Picture Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomTextMode: "    & CStr(obj.CustomTextMode  ) ' Custom Picture Text Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureID: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureID & """" ' Background Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureID: """ & obj.CustomPictureID & """" ' Custom Picture ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureFile: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureFile & """" ' Background Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureFile: """ & obj.CustomPictureFile & """" ' Custom Picture File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomShapeType: "   & CStr(obj.CustomShapeType ) ' Custom Shape Type

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubObjects: """      & obj.SubObjects      & """" ' Sub-objects Blob
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconMode: "          & CStr(obj.IconMode        ) ' Icon Mode

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubSymbolsLayout: """ & obj.SubSymbolsLayout & """" ' Sub-Symbols Layout
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMProcedureSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdPDMReferenceSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdPDM Reference Symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Diagram: "           & CStrObj(obj.Diagram      ) ' Diagram
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Symbol Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Hidden: "            & CStr(obj.Hidden          ) ' Hidden
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Height: "            & CStr(obj.Height          ) ' Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "RelatedPosition: "   & obj.RelatedPosition.AsText  ' Related Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DashStyle: "         & CStr(obj.DashStyle       ) ' Dash Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ListOfPoints: "      & obj.ListOfPoints.AsText     ' List Points
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CornerStyle: "       & CStr(obj.CornerStyle     ) ' Corner Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ArrowStyle: "        & CStr(obj.ArrowStyle      ) ' Arrows
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkPosition: "      & obj.LinkPosition.AsText     ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkSize: "          & obj.LinkSize.AsText         ' Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceSymbol: "      & CStrObj(obj.SourceSymbol ) ' Source Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationSymbol: " & CStrObj(obj.DestinationSymbol) ' Destination Symbol
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CenterTextOffset: "  & obj.CenterTextOffset.AsText ' Centered Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceTextOffset: "  & obj.SourceTextOffset.AsText ' Source Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DestinationTextOffset: " & obj.DestinationTextOffset.AsText ' Destination Text Offset
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FontList: """        & obj.FontList        & """" ' Font List
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object: "            & CStrObj(obj.Object       ) ' Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SymbolContent: """   & obj.SymbolContent   & """" ' Symbol Content
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubSymbolsLayout: """ & obj.SubSymbolsLayout & """" ' Sub-Symbols Layout
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdPDMReferenceSymbol = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Workload4: "         & CStr(obj.Workload4       ) ' Workload 4

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AllocatedUsers: """  & obj.AllocatedUsers  & """" ' Allocated Users
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Type: """            & obj.Type            & """" ' Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Priority: "          & CStr(obj.Priority        ) ' Priority
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Status: "            & CStr(obj.Status          ) ' Status
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Risk: "              & CStr(obj.Risk            ) ' Risk
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "VerificationMethod: """ & obj.VerificationMethod & """" ' Verification Method
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdRQMRequirement = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdRQMTraceabilityLink(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdRQM Traceability Link

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object2: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object2      ) ' Second Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Object1: "           & CStrObj(obj.Object1      ) ' First Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkedObject: "      & CStrObj(obj.LinkedObject ) ' Linked Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkType: """        & obj.LinkType        & """" ' Link Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Bookmark: """        & obj.Bookmark        & """" ' Bookmark
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkedObjectClassName: """ & obj.LinkedObjectClassName & """" ' Linked Object Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkedObjectClassKind: " & CStr(obj.LinkedObjectClassKind) ' Linked Object Class Kind
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DesignObject: "      & CStr(obj.DesignObject    ) ' Design Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExternalDocument: "  & CStr(obj.ExternalDocument) ' External File
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "InternalRequirement: " & CStr(obj.InternalRequirement) ' Internal Requirement
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LinkedObjectTargetModel: " & CStrObj(obj.LinkedObjectTargetModel) ' Linked Object Target Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Requirement: "       & CStrObj(obj.Requirement  ) ' Parent Requirement
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdRQMTraceabilityLink = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ReverseCreateSymbol: " & CStr(obj.ReverseCreateSymbol) ' Reverse Engineering Create Symbols

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ReverseShowElement: " & CStr(obj.ReverseShowElement) ' Reverse Engineering Show Elements
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ReverseShowGroup: "  & CStr(obj.ReverseShowGroup) ' Reverse Engineering Show Groups
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ReverseShowComplexType: " & CStr(obj.ReverseShowComplexType) ' Reverse Engineering Show Complex Types
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ReverseShowSimpleType: " & CStr(obj.ReverseShowSimpleType) ' Reverse Engineering Show Simple Types
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ReverseConvertReference: " & CStr(obj.ReverseConvertReference) ' Reverse Engineering Convert Unique References
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FolderCheck: "       & CStrObj(obj.FolderCheck  ) ' Check Folders
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SubFolderCheck: "    & CStr(obj.SubFolderCheck  ) ' Check Subfolders
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdXSMFolderOptions = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdXSMXMLDiagram(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdXSM XML Model Diagram

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Code: """            & obj.Code            & """" ' Code
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayPreferences: """ & obj.DisplayPreferences & """" ' Display Preferences
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Scale: "             & CStr(obj.Scale           ) ' Scale
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PaperSize: "         & obj.PaperSize.AsText        ' Paper Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PaperSource: "       & CStr(obj.PaperSource     ) ' Paper Source
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageMargins: "       & obj.PageMargins.AsText      ' Page Margins
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageFormat: "        & CStr(obj.PageFormat      ) ' Page Format
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageOrientation: "   & CStr(obj.PageOrientation ) ' Page Orientation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Diagram Flags
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageFooterTemplate: """ & obj.PageFooterTemplate & """" ' Page Footer Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageHeaderTemplate: """ & obj.PageHeaderTemplate & """" ' Page Header Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PageNumberTemplate: """ & obj.PageNumberTemplate & """" ' Page Number Template
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SwimlaneHeaderHeight: " & CStr(obj.SwimlaneHeaderHeight) ' Swimlane Header Height
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SetAsDefault: "      & CStr(obj.SetAsDefault    ) ' Is Default
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdXSMXMLDiagram = Desc

End Function

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayName: """     & obj.DisplayName     & """" ' Display Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DisplayTypeName: """ & obj.DisplayTypeName & """" ' Displayed Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ReferenceName: """   & obj.ReferenceName   & """" ' Reference
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Reference: "         & CStrObj(obj.Reference    ) ' Reference Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UsesAnyAttribute: "  & CStr(obj.UsesAnyAttribute) ' Any Attribute
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AnyAttribute: "      & CStrObj(obj.AnyAttribute ) ' Any Attribute Object
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdXSMAttributeGroup = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdXSMComplexContent(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdXSM Complex Content

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "OverallModificationDate: " & CStr(obj.OverallModificationDate) ' Overall Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Model: "             & CStrObj(obj.Model        ) ' Model
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SourceReplication: " & CStrObj(obj.SourceReplication) ' Original Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ExtendedAttributesText: """ & obj.ExtendedAttributesText & """" ' Extended Attributes
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Stereotype: """      & obj.Stereotype      & """" ' Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotype: """ & obj.MetaClassStereotype & """" ' Metaclass Stereotype
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "StereotypeObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.StereotypeObject) ' Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClassStereotypeObject: " & CStrObj(obj.MetaClassStereotypeObject) ' Metaclass Stereotype Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ID: """              & obj.ID              & """" ' ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "HasAnnotation: "     & CStr(obj.HasAnnotation   ) ' Has Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AnnotationID: """    & obj.AnnotationID    & """" ' Annotation ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AnnotationObject: "  & CStrObj(obj.AnnotationObject) ' Annotation Object
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "History: """         & obj.History         & """" ' History
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Mixed: "             & CStr(obj.Mixed           ) ' Mixed
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdXSMComplexContent = Desc

End Function

Function DescribePdXSMImport(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdXSM Import

   Else

   End If

Function DescribePdXSMPatternFacet(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdXSM Pattern Facet

   Dim Desc

   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator

Function DescribePdXSMNotation(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdXSM Notation

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date

Function DescribePdXSMDocumentation(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdXSM Documentation

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientEndColor: "  & CStr(obj.GradientEndColor) ' Gradient End Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PictureFillMode: "   & CStr(obj.PictureFillMode ) ' Picture Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AutoAdjustToText: "  & CStr(obj.AutoAdjustToText) ' Auto Adjust to Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ManuallyResized: "   & CStr(obj.ManuallyResized ) ' Resized
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepAspect: "        & CStr(obj.KeepAspect      ) ' Keep Aspect Ratio
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepCenter: "        & CStr(obj.KeepCenter      ) ' Keep Center
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepSize: "          & CStr(obj.KeepSize        ) ' Keep Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureType: " & CStr(obj.CustomPictureType) ' Custom Picture Type

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureID: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureID & """" ' Background Picture ID

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BackgroundPictureFile: """ & obj.BackgroundPictureFile & """" ' Background Picture File

      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdXSMComplexTypeSymbol = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdXSMSimpleTypeSymbol(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdXSM Simple Type Symbol

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Rect: "              & obj.Rect.AsText             ' Rect
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Flags: "             & CStr(obj.Flags           ) ' Flag
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Symbol Name

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Position: "          & obj.Position.AsText         ' Position
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Size: "              & obj.Size.AsText             ' Size

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Protected: "         & CStr(obj.Protected       ) ' Protected

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Width: "             & CStr(obj.Width           ) ' Width

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineColor: "         & CStr(obj.LineColor       ) ' Line Color

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "LineWidth: "         & CStr(obj.LineWidth       ) ' Line Width
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Shadow: "            & CStr(obj.Shadow          ) ' Shadow
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowStyle: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowStyle     ) ' Shadow Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShadowColor: "       & CStr(obj.ShadowColor     ) ' Shadow Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Transparent: "       & CStr(obj.Transparent     ) ' Transparent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "FillColor: "         & CStr(obj.FillColor       ) ' Fill Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "BrushStyle: "        & CStr(obj.BrushStyle      ) ' Brush Style
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientFillMode: "  & CStr(obj.GradientFillMode) ' Gradient Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GradientEndColor: "  & CStr(obj.GradientEndColor) ' Gradient End Color
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "PictureFillMode: "   & CStr(obj.PictureFillMode ) ' Picture Fill Mode
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "AutoAdjustToText: "  & CStr(obj.AutoAdjustToText) ' Auto Adjust to Text
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ManuallyResized: "   & CStr(obj.ManuallyResized ) ' Resized
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepAspect: "        & CStr(obj.KeepAspect      ) ' Keep Aspect Ratio
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepCenter: "        & CStr(obj.KeepCenter      ) ' Keep Center
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "KeepSize: "          & CStr(obj.KeepSize        ) ' Keep Size
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CustomPictureType: " & CStr(obj.CustomPictureType) ' Custom Picture Type

Function DescribePdXSMClassMapping(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdXSM Class Mapping

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectID: """        & obj.ObjectID        & """" ' Object ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "CreationDate: "      & CStr(obj.CreationDate    ) ' Creation Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Creator: """         & obj.Creator         & """" ' Creator
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ModificationDate: "  & CStr(obj.ModificationDate) ' Modification Date
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Modifier: """        & obj.Modifier        & """" ' Modifier

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Replica: "           & CStr(obj.Replica         ) ' Replica

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Description: """     & obj.Description     & """" ' Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotation: """      & obj.Annotation      & """" ' Annotation
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Annotated: "         & CStr(obj.Annotated       ) ' Annotated
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Preview: """         & obj.Preview         & """" ' Code Preview

         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "GenerationOrigin: "  & CStrObj(obj.GenerationOrigin) ' Generation Origin
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Criteria: """        & obj.Criteria        & """" ' Criteria
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Expression: """      & obj.Expression      & """" ' Expression
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "SelectStatement: """ & obj.SelectStatement & """" ' Select
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "InsertStatement: """ & obj.InsertStatement & """" ' Insert
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UpdateStatement: """ & obj.UpdateStatement & """" ' Update
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DeleteStatement: """ & obj.DeleteStatement & """" ' Delete
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Classifier: "        & CStrObj(obj.Classifier   ) ' Classifier
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "DataSource: "        & CStrObj(obj.DataSource   ) ' Data Source
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MappedTo: """        & obj.MappedTo        & """" ' Mapped to
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ComplexType: "       & CStrObj(obj.ComplexType  ) ' ComplexType
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdXSMExternalComplexTypeMapping = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribePdXSMCheckModelComponentCategory(obj)
' Build a the full text description of a PdXSM Object Check Category

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Parent: "            & CStrObj(obj.Parent       ) ' Parent
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassName: """       & obj.ClassName       & """" ' Class Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectType: """      & obj.ObjectType      & """" ' Object Type
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Folder: "            & CStrObj(obj.Folder       ) ' Parent Folder
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Package: "           & CStrObj(obj.Package      ) ' Parent Package
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassKind: "         & CStr(obj.ClassKind       ) ' Object Class ID
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ShortDescription: """ & obj.ShortDescription & """" ' Short Description
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ObjectLocation: """  & obj.ObjectLocation  & """" ' Object Location
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "UOL: """             & obj.UOL             & """" ' Unique Object Location
         'esc = Desc&vbCrLf& "IconPicture: "       & obj.IconPicture ' Icon
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "MetaClass: "         & CStrObj(obj.MetaClass    ) ' Metaclass
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Path: """            & obj.Path            & """" ' Path
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Controler: "         & CStrObj(obj.Controler    ) ' Controller
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Name: """            & obj.Name            & """" ' Name
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Comment: """         & obj.Comment         & """" ' Comment
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "Header: """          & obj.Header          & """" ' Header
         Desc = Desc&vbCrLf& "ClassID: "           & CStr(obj.ClassID         ) ' Listed Objects Class Identifier
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribePdXSMCheckModelComponentCategory = Desc

End Function 

Function DescribeAnyObject(obj)
' Build a the full text description of any known object

   Dim Desc
   Desc = ""
   If IsEmpty(obj) Then
      Desc = "<Empty!>"
   ElseIf IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         Desc = "<Nothing>"
      Else
         Select Case obj.ClassKind
            Case PdCommon.cls_ProgressDialog
               Desc = DescribePdCommonProgressDialog(obj)
            Case PdCommon.cls_ProgressStatusBar
               Desc = DescribePdCommonProgressStatusBar(obj)
            Case PdCommon.cls_ApplicationModule
               Desc = DescribePdCommonApplicationModule(obj)
            Case PdCommon.cls_ResourceFile
               Desc = DescribePdCommonResourceFile(obj)
            Case PdCommon.cls_MetaModel
               Desc = DescribePdCommonMetaModel(obj)
            Case PdCommon.cls_MetaLibrary
               Desc = DescribePdCommonMetaLibrary(obj)
            Case PdCommon.cls_MetaAttribute
               Desc = DescribePdCommonMetaAttribute(obj)
            Case PdCommon.cls_MetaCollection
               Desc = DescribePdCommonMetaCollection(obj)
            Case PdCommon.cls_MetaClass
               Desc = DescribePdCommonMetaClass(obj)
            Case PdCommon.cls_Shortcut
               Desc = DescribePdCommonShortcut(obj)
            Case PdCommon.cls_TargetModel
               Desc = DescribePdCommonTargetModel(obj)
            Case PdCommon.cls_SubReplication
               Desc = DescribePdCommonSubReplication(obj)
            Case PdCommon.cls_Replication
               Desc = DescribePdCommonReplication(obj)
            Case PdCommon.cls_PolygonSymbol
               Desc = DescribePdCommonPolygonSymbol(obj)
            Case PdCommon.cls_PolylineSymbol
               Desc = DescribePdCommonPolylineSymbol(obj)
            Case PdCommon.cls_ArcSymbol
               Desc = DescribePdCommonArcSymbol(obj)
            Case PdCommon.cls_RectangleSymbol
               Desc = DescribePdCommonRectangleSymbol(obj)

               Desc = DescribePdXSMKeyRef(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_Unique
               Desc = DescribePdXSMUnique(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_Notation
               Desc = DescribePdXSMNotation(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_Group
               Desc = DescribePdXSMGroup(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_Any
               Desc = DescribePdXSMAny(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_Element
               Desc = DescribePdXSMElement(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_GroupParticle
               Desc = DescribePdXSMGroupParticle(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_Selector
               Desc = DescribePdXSMSelector(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_ComplexType
               Desc = DescribePdXSMComplexType(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_SimpleType
               Desc = DescribePdXSMSimpleType(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_Annotation
               Desc = DescribePdXSMAnnotation(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_AppInfo
               Desc = DescribePdXSMAppInfo(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_Documentation
               Desc = DescribePdXSMDocumentation(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_XmlNamespace
               Desc = DescribePdXSMXmlNamespace(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_Model
               Desc = DescribePdXSMModel(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_SchemaLanguage
               Desc = DescribePdXSMSchemaLanguage(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_ElementSymbol
               Desc = DescribePdXSMElementSymbol(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_ComplexTypeSymbol
               Desc = DescribePdXSMComplexTypeSymbol(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_SimpleTypeSymbol
               Desc = DescribePdXSMSimpleTypeSymbol(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_AnySymbol
               Desc = DescribePdXSMAnySymbol(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_ItemGroupSymbol
               Desc = DescribePdXSMItemGroupSymbol(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_GroupParticleSymbol
               Desc = DescribePdXSMGroupParticleSymbol(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_DataSource
               Desc = DescribePdXSMDataSource(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_ElementMapping
               Desc = DescribePdXSMElementMapping(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_ComplexTypeMapping
               Desc = DescribePdXSMComplexTypeMapping(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_AttributeMapping
               Desc = DescribePdXSMAttributeMapping(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_TableMapping
               Desc = DescribePdXSMTableMapping(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_TableColumnMapping
               Desc = DescribePdXSMTableColumnMapping(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_ClassMapping
               Desc = DescribePdXSMClassMapping(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_ClassAttributeMapping
               Desc = DescribePdXSMClassAttributeMapping(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_ExternalElementMapping
               Desc = DescribePdXSMExternalElementMapping(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_ExternalAttributeMapping
               Desc = DescribePdXSMExternalAttributeMapping(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_ExternalComplexTypeMapping
               Desc = DescribePdXSMExternalComplexTypeMapping(obj)
            Case PdXSM.cls_CheckModelComponentCategory
               Desc = DescribePdXSMCheckModelComponentCategory(obj)
            Case Else
               Desc = "<Unknown object!>"
         End Select
      End If
   Else
      Desc = "<Not an object!>"
   End If

   DescribeAnyObject = Desc

End Function

Function CStrObj(obj)
' Helper: produces a brief text describing an object

   If IsObject(obj) Then
      If obj Is Nothing Then
         CStrObj = "<Nothing>"
      ElseIf obj.HasAttribute("Name") Then
         CStrObj = obj.ClassName & ": """ & obj.Name & """"
      Else
         CStrObj = obj.ClassName
      End If
   Else
      If IsEmpty(obj) Then
         CStrObj = "<Empty>"
      Else
         If IsNull(obj) Then
            CStrObj = "<Null>"
         Else
            CStrObj = "<Not a valid object!>"
         End If
      End If
   End If
End Function
